#: .\achievements.json
msgid "<color_red>Ghost Hunter</color>"
msgstr "<color_red>幽灵猎手</color>"

#. ~ Description for <color_red>Ghost Hunter</color>
#: .\achievements.json
msgid "Kill 10 Ghost Harvesters, 10 Ghost Trappers and 10 Ghost Seekers."
msgstr "击杀10个幽灵收割者、10个幽灵陷阱者和10个幽灵搜寻者。"

#: .\achievements.json
msgid "<color_red>Fires in the sky</color>"
msgstr "<color_red>天空之火</color>"

#. ~ Description for <color_red>Fires in the sky</color>
#: .\achievements.json
msgid "Trigger the Gala Event."
msgstr "触发庆典事件。"

#: .\achievements.json
msgid "<color_red>Treasure of the Old World</color>"
msgstr "<color_red>旧世界的宝藏</color>"

#. ~ Description for <color_red>Treasure of the Old World</color>
#. ~ Description for mission '{'str': 'Heist of the Centuries'}'
#: .\achievements.json .\npcs\missions.json
msgid "Crack the Sierra Madre open."
msgstr "撬开塞拉马德雷。"

#: .\achievements.json
msgid "<color_red>Stimpacked</color>"
msgstr "<color_red>兴奋剂强化</color>"

#. ~ Description for <color_red>Stimpacked</color>
#: .\achievements.json
msgid "Heal your wounds instantly with the regenerating power of a stimpack."
msgstr "利用兴奋剂的再生力量瞬间治愈你的伤口。"

#: .\achievements.json
msgid "<color_red>Taste of Cloud</color>"
msgstr "<color_red>云之滋味</color>"

#. ~ Description for <color_red>Taste of Cloud</color>
#: .\achievements.json
msgid "Drink Sierra Madre martini."
msgstr "饮用马德雷山脉马提尼。"

#: .\achievements.json
msgid "<color_red>Sneaky sneaky</color>"
msgstr "<color_red>潜行匿踪</color>"

#. ~ Description for <color_red>Sneaky sneaky</color>
#: .\achievements.json
msgid "Hide from sight of other creatures by using the Stealth Boy."
msgstr "使用隐形小子躲避其他生物的视线。"

#: .\achievements.json
msgid "<color_red>Ghost Sight</color>"
msgstr "<color_red>幽灵视界</color>"

#. ~ Description for <color_red>Ghost Sight</color>
#: .\achievements.json
msgid "See the way Ghost People see."
msgstr "以幽灵人的视角观察世界。"

#: .\achievements.json
msgid "<color_red>The Power of Mind</color>"
msgstr "<color_red>心灵之力</color>"

#. ~ Description for <color_red>The Power of Mind</color>
#: .\achievements.json
msgid "Take some Mentats and see the true colors of the world."
msgstr "服用曼他特，看清世界的真实色彩。"

#: .\achievements.json
msgid "<color_red>Last Luxuries</color>"
msgstr "<color_red>最后的奢侈</color>"

#. ~ Description for <color_red>Last Luxuries</color>
#: .\achievements.json
msgid "Relieve the horrible pain of the Old World..."
msgstr "缓解旧世界的可怕痛苦……"

#: .\achievements.json
msgid "<color_red>Try to leave and BOOM</color>"
msgstr "<color_red>试图离开，然后——轰！</color>"

#. ~ Description for <color_red>Try to leave and BOOM</color>
#: .\achievements.json
msgid "Disobey orders."
msgstr "违抗命令。"

#: .\effects.json
msgid "Sierra Madre gas intoxication"
msgstr "马德雷山脉毒气中毒"

#. ~ Description of effect 'Sierra Madre gas intoxication'.
#: .\effects.json
msgid "You have been exposed to a dense pocket of the Sierra Madre toxic gas!"
msgstr "你暴露在了一团高浓度的马德雷山脉毒气中！"

#. ~ Apply message for effect(s) 'Sierra Madre gas intoxication'.
#: .\effects.json
msgid "The highly concentrated Sierra Madre toxic gas surrounds you..."
msgstr "高浓度的马德雷山脉毒气正包围着你……"

#. ~ Remove message for effect(s) 'Sierra Madre gas intoxication'.
#: .\effects.json
msgid "You've managed to get out of the concentrated gas pocket in time..."
msgstr "你及时脱离了那团高浓度毒气……"

#. ~ Miss message for effect(s) 'Sierra Madre gas intoxication'.
#: .\effects.json
msgid "Your body burns on the inside!"
msgstr "你的体内在燃烧！"

#: .\effects.json
msgid "Sierra Madre Cloud expousure"
msgstr "马德雷山脉红云暴露"

#. ~ Description of effect 'Sierra Madre Cloud expousure'.
#: .\effects.json
msgid ""
"The Cloud of red, poisonous gas engulfing Sierra Madre slowly corrodes your "
"body."
msgstr "笼罩马德雷山脉的红色毒云正缓慢侵蚀你的身体。"

#. ~ Apply message for effect(s) 'Sierra Madre Cloud expousure'.
#: .\effects.json
msgid ""
"You've found yourself in the Sierra Madre. The red sky and the smell of "
"copper and Old World gold indicate the contamination of the air by a lethal "
"gas..."
msgstr "你发现自己身处马德雷山脉。红色的天空、铜与旧世界黄金的气味，都表明空气中弥漫着致命的毒气……"

#. ~ Miss message for effect(s) 'Sierra Madre Cloud expousure'.
#: .\effects.json
msgid "You feel an unpleasant, burning sensation under your skin..."
msgstr "你感到皮肤下有一种令人不适的灼烧感……"

#. ~ Miss message for effect(s) 'Sierra Madre Cloud expousure'.
#: .\effects.json
msgid "Your lungs pain you and you struggle a bit to breathe..."
msgstr "你的肺部疼痛，呼吸有些困难……"

#: .\effects.json .\spells.json
msgid "Cloud Kiss intoxication (weak)"
msgstr "云吻中毒（轻微）"

#. ~ Description of effect 'Cloud Kiss intoxication (weak)'.
#: .\effects.json
msgid ""
"The Cloud Kiss venom has found a way into your body. While the doses's been "
"fairly weak, it still makes you suffer a lot."
msgstr "云吻毒液已侵入你的身体。虽然剂量相当轻微，但仍让你痛苦不堪。"

#. ~ Miss message for effect(s) 'Cloud Kiss intoxication (weak)'.
#. ~ Miss message for effect(s) 'Cloud Kiss intoxication (potent)'.
#. ~ Miss message for effect(s) 'Cloud Kiss intoxication (lethal)'.
#. ~ Miss message for effect(s) 'Cloud venom intoxication (weak)'.
#. ~ Miss message for effect(s) 'Cloud venom intoxication (potent)'.
#. ~ Miss message for effect(s) 'Cloud venom intoxication (lethal)'.
#: .\effects.json
msgid "Your throat burns!"
msgstr "你的喉咙在燃烧！"

#. ~ Miss message for effect(s) 'Cloud Kiss intoxication (weak)'.
#. ~ Miss message for effect(s) 'Cloud Kiss intoxication (potent)'.
#. ~ Miss message for effect(s) 'Cloud Kiss intoxication (lethal)'.
#. ~ Miss message for effect(s) 'Cloud venom intoxication (weak)'.
#. ~ Miss message for effect(s) 'Cloud venom intoxication (potent)'.
#. ~ Miss message for effect(s) 'Cloud venom intoxication (lethal)'.
#: .\effects.json
msgid "You feel as if there was burning napalm inside your stomach!"
msgstr "你感觉胃里仿佛有燃烧的凝固汽油！"

#: .\effects.json .\spells.json
msgid "Cloud Kiss intoxication (potent)"
msgstr "云吻中毒（强烈）"

#. ~ Description of effect 'Cloud Kiss intoxication (potent)'.
#: .\effects.json
msgid ""
"The Cloud Kiss venom has found a way into your body. It's concentrated "
"enough to make you feel like dying and it might kill you if you're too weak "
"to handle it."
msgstr "云吻毒液已侵入你的身体。浓度之高让你感觉濒临死亡，若你过于虚弱无法承受，它可能会要了你的命。"

#: .\effects.json .\spells.json
msgid "Cloud Kiss intoxication (lethal)"
msgstr "云吻中毒（致命）"

#. ~ Description of effect 'Cloud Kiss intoxication (lethal)'.
#: .\effects.json
msgid ""
"The Cloud Kiss venom has found a way into your body. It's concentrated "
"enough to straight-up kill you. Say goodbye to this cruel world..."
msgstr "云吻毒液已侵入你的身体。其浓度足以直接杀死你。向这个残酷的世界告别吧……"

#: .\effects.json
msgid "Eaten raw flesh of a Ghost"
msgstr "生食幽灵人肉"

#. ~ Description of effect 'Eaten raw flesh of a Ghost'.
#: .\effects.json
msgid ""
"The starvation and desperation brought you to eating Ghost People flesh "
"straight from their bodies, raw. You feel the Sierra Madre toxins running "
"through your veins..."
msgstr "饥饿与绝望迫使你直接从幽灵人身上生食其肉。你感到马德雷山脉的毒素在血管中流淌……"

#. ~ Miss message for effect(s) 'Eaten raw flesh of a Ghost'.
#. ~ Miss message for effect(s) 'Eaten prepared flesh of a Ghost'.
#: .\effects.json
msgid "You feel as if someone was gutting you alive!"
msgstr "你感觉仿佛有人正在活生生地剖开你的内脏！"

#: .\effects.json
msgid "Eaten prepared flesh of a Ghost"
msgstr "食用处理过的幽灵人肉"

#. ~ Description of effect 'Eaten prepared flesh of a Ghost'.
#: .\effects.json
msgid ""
"The starvation and desperation brought you to eating Ghost People flesh. "
"You've prepared it, but still feel the Sierra Madre toxins running through "
"your veins..."
msgstr "饥饿与绝望迫使你食用幽灵人肉。你已将其处理过，但仍感到马德雷山脉的毒素在血管中流淌……"

#: .\effects.json
msgid "Drank Sierra Madre Martini"
msgstr "饮用马德雷山脉马提尼"

#. ~ Description of effect 'Drank Sierra Madre Martini'.
#: .\effects.json
msgid ""
"This martini tasted awful, but seems to strenghten you and help your body "
"tissues regenerate. Apparently the Cloud can both deteriorate and "
"regenerate, the latter you can easily observe on Ghost People. The right "
"combination of ingredients allowed you to utilize the regenerative potential"
" for yourself."
msgstr ""
"这杯马提尼味道糟糕，但似乎能增强你的力量并帮助身体组织再生。显然，云层既能导致恶化也能促进再生，后者你可以在幽灵人身上轻易观察到。正确的成分组合让你得以利用这种再生潜力为己所用。"

#. ~ Miss message for effect(s) 'Drank Sierra Madre Martini'.
#: .\effects.json
msgid ""
"You feel mysterious strength empowering your entire body, boosting its "
"healing capability."
msgstr "你感到一股神秘的力量充盈全身，提升了你的愈合能力。"

#: .\effects.json
msgid "Injected stimpack"
msgstr "注射治疗针"

#. ~ Description of effect 'Injected stimpack'.
#: .\effects.json
msgid ""
"As opposed to the post-apocalyptic wasteland, upon injecting the stimpack "
"you feel like coming back to life and shining with glory of a true survivor."
msgstr "与后末日废土不同，注射治疗针后，你感觉重获新生，闪耀着真正幸存者的荣光。"

#. ~ Miss message for effect(s) 'Injected stimpack'.
#: .\effects.json
msgid "You feel alive, so alive... It's beautiful."
msgstr "你感到充满生机，如此鲜活……这感觉美妙无比。"

#: .\effects.json
msgid "Took Mentats"
msgstr "服用曼他特"

#. ~ Description of effect 'Took Mentats'.
#: .\effects.json
msgid ""
"Your mind clears, your thought capacity increases, your vision sharpens. Now"
" you see the truth..."
msgstr "你的思维变得清晰，思考能力增强，视觉变得锐利。现在你看到了真相……"

#: .\effects.json
msgid "Injected Med-X"
msgstr "注射医疗-X"

#. ~ Description of effect 'Injected Med-X'.
#: .\effects.json
msgid "Your pain is being washed away and you feel stronger and more immune."
msgstr "你的疼痛正在消退，你感到更强壮且更具免疫力。"

#: .\effects.json .\spells.json
msgid "Stealth Field"
msgstr "潜行力场"

#. ~ Description of effect 'Stealth Field'.
#: .\effects.json
msgid ""
"The light bends and reflects around you hiding you from observers' eyes."
msgstr "光线在你周围弯曲反射，将你隐藏在观察者的视线之外。"

#. ~ Apply message for effect(s) 'Stealth Field'.
#: .\effects.json
msgid "You activate the Stealth Boy and hide behind the Stealth Field."
msgstr "你启动了潜行小子，隐藏在潜行力场之后。"

#. ~ Remove message for effect(s) 'Stealth Field'.
#: .\effects.json
msgid "You're no longer hidden behind the Stealth Field."
msgstr "你不再隐藏在潜行力场之后。"

#: .\effects.json .\spells.json .\items\consumables.json
msgid "Ghost Sight"
msgid_plural "Flasks of Ghost Sight"
msgstr[0] "幽灵视野"

#. ~ Description of effect 'Ghost Sight'.
#: .\effects.json
msgid ""
"Your throat burns after drinking the Ghost Sight, but now you can clearly "
"see through the darkness."
msgstr "饮用幽灵视野后，你的喉咙灼烧，但现在你能清晰地看透黑暗。"

#. ~ Apply message for effect(s) 'Ghost Sight'.
#: .\effects.json
msgid "You drink Ghost Sight and your eyes quickly adjust to the darkness."
msgstr "你饮下幽灵视野，双眼迅速适应了黑暗。"

#. ~ Remove message for effect(s) 'Ghost Sight'.
#: .\effects.json
msgid ""
"The effect of Ghost Sight wears off and you're back to your standard (lack "
"of) nightvision."
msgstr "幽灵视野的效果消退，你恢复了标准（缺乏）的夜视能力。"

#: .\effects.json
msgid "Sierra Madre Treasure Hunter"
msgstr "马德雷山脉宝藏猎人"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Sierra Madre Treasure Hunter'}
#: .\effects.json
msgid ""
"You're one of the many survivors who set on cracking the Sierra Madre open "
"and finding the treasure of the Old World buried deep inside its vault."
msgstr "你是众多幸存者之一，决心破解马德雷山脉，寻找深藏在其金库中的旧世界宝藏。"

#: .\effects.json
msgid "Sierra Madre Casino Guest"
msgstr "马德雷山脉赌场宾客"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Sierra Madre Casino Guest'}
#: .\effects.json
msgid ""
"You're one of a couple survivors who saw the Sierra Madre Casino after the "
"apocalypse came... Now you only need to get to the vault to claim the "
"treasure of the Old World."
msgstr "你是少数在末日降临后目睹马德雷山脉赌场的幸存者之一……现在你只需进入金库，就能索取旧世界的宝藏。"

#: .\effects.json
msgid "Sierra Madre Conqueror"
msgstr "马德雷山脉征服者"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Sierra Madre Conqueror'}
#: .\effects.json
msgid ""
"And so you've cracked the Sierra Madre open, finally, after all you've been "
"through you've uncovered its deepest secrets."
msgstr "于是，你终于破解了马德雷山脉，历经一切后，你揭开了它最深的秘密。"

#: .\effects.json
msgid "Sierra Madre Gala leader"
msgstr "马德雷山脉庆典领袖"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Sierra Madre Gala leader'}
#: .\effects.json
msgid ""
"You've managed to successfully trigger the Gala Event, opening the door to "
"the Sierra Madre Casino. Now it is time to enter this legendary resort."
msgstr "你已成功触发庆典事件，打开了通往锡耶拉马德雷赌场的大门。现在，是时候进入这座传奇度假胜地了。"

#: .\effects.json
msgid "The collar on your neck explodes, tearing your head apart!"
msgstr "你脖子上的项圈爆炸了，将你的头颅撕成碎片！"

#: .\effects.json
msgid "Cloud venom intoxication (weak)"
msgstr "云毒中毒（轻微）"

#. ~ Description of effect 'Cloud venom intoxication (weak)'.
#: .\effects.json
msgid ""
"The venom made out of the Sierra Madre Cloud is running through yoru veins, "
"burning you from the inside. The dose doesn't seem to be lethal, but you "
"still feel like shit."
msgstr "由锡耶拉马德雷云雾制成的毒液正流经你的血管，从内部灼烧着你。剂量似乎不致命，但你仍感觉糟透了。"

#: .\effects.json
msgid "Cloud venom intoxication (potent)"
msgstr "云毒中毒（强效）"

#. ~ Description of effect 'Cloud venom intoxication (potent)'.
#: .\effects.json
msgid ""
"The venom made out of the Sierra Madre Cloud is running through yoru veins, "
"burning you from the inside. The dose is potent and might seriously wreck "
"your health or even kill you if your organism is too weak to handle it."
msgstr "由锡耶拉马德雷云雾制成的毒液正流经你的血管，从内部灼烧着你。剂量强效，若你的身体过于虚弱无法承受，可能会严重损害健康甚至致命。"

#: .\effects.json
msgid "Cloud venom intoxication (lethal)"
msgstr "云毒中毒（致命）"

#. ~ Description of effect 'Cloud venom intoxication (lethal)'.
#: .\effects.json
msgid ""
"The venom made out of the Sierra Madre Cloud is running through yoru veins, "
"burning you from the inside. You feel it in your guts that it won't end well"
" for you..."
msgstr "由锡耶拉马德雷云雾制成的毒液正流经你的血管，从内部灼烧着你。你从心底感到，这对你来说不会有好结果……"

#: .\items_NPC_missions.json
msgid "Hologram Projector - Locator of Sierra Madre Casino"
msgid_plural "Hologram Projector - Locator of Sierra Madre Casinos"
msgstr[0] "全息投影仪 - 锡耶拉马德雷赌场定位器"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Hologram Projector - Locator of Sierra Madre
#. Casino'}
#: .\items_NPC_missions.json
msgid ""
"This is a hologram projector which generates an interactive hologram when "
"you activate it. Hologram can talk to you, answer some of your questions, "
"but most importantly, it can locate Sierra Madre Casino"
msgstr "这是一台全息投影仪，激活时会生成一个交互式全息影像。全息影像可以与你交谈，回答你的一些问题，但最重要的是，它能定位锡耶拉马德雷赌场。"

#: .\modinfo.json
msgid "<color_red>Sierra Madre</color>"
msgstr "<color_red>锡耶拉马德雷</color>"

#. ~ Description for <color_red>Sierra Madre</color>
#: .\modinfo.json
msgid ""
"Adds the (in)famous villa and casino of the <color_red>Sierra Madre</color> "
"which can be found via an abandoned bunker from Fallout New Vegas: Dead "
"Money."
msgstr "添加了（声名狼藉的）<color_red>锡耶拉马德雷</color>别墅与赌场，可通过《辐射：新维加斯 - 死钱》中的废弃掩体找到。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Stealth Field'}
#: .\spells.json
msgid ""
"The Stealth Field makes the user blend in with the surroundings by "
"reflecting light in a way that makes it look as if no one was standing where"
" the user is."
msgstr "隐形力场通过反射光线使使用者融入周围环境，看起来就像使用者所在的位置空无一人。"

#. ~ Message for SPELL '{'str': 'Stealth Field'}'
#: .\spells.json
msgid "You hide behind the Stealth Field..."
msgstr "你隐藏在隐形力场之后……"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Ghost Sight'}
#: .\spells.json
msgid ""
"Drinking the Ghost Sight isn't very healthy for you, but allows you to see "
"in the same way as Ghost People do - darkness won't be a problem anymore."
msgstr "饮用幽灵视野对你并不健康，但能让你以幽灵族的方式视物——黑暗将不再是问题。"

#. ~ Message for SPELL '{'str': 'Ghost Sight'}'
#: .\spells.json
msgid ""
"Your vision sharpens, allowing you to see the world the way Ghost People do."
msgstr "你的视觉变得敏锐，让你能以幽灵族的方式观察世界。"

#: .\spells.json
msgid "unlocking the Sierra Madre Casino vault entrance"
msgstr "解锁锡耶拉马德雷赌场金库入口"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'unlocking the Sierra Madre Casino vault
#. entrance'}
#: .\spells.json
msgid ""
"Playing the recorded Vera Keyes' voice at the intercom near the vault door "
"will allow you to trigger its unlocking mechanism."
msgstr "在金库门附近的内部通话系统播放薇拉·凯斯的录音，可触发其解锁机制。"

#. ~ Message for SPELL '{'str': 'unlocking the Sierra Madre Casino vault
#. entrance'}'
#: .\spells.json
msgid ""
"You play the recorded sound of Vera Keyes containing the vault entrance "
"password."
msgstr "你播放了包含金库入口密码的薇拉·凯斯录音。"

#: .\spells.json
msgid "There's no door to unlock nearby."
msgstr "附近没有可解锁的门。"

#: .\spells.json
msgid ""
"The door has been unlocked... Finally... After all you've been through, the "
"Sierra Madre has opened its vault right in front of you. Madre is yours "
"yours yours..."
msgstr "门已解锁……终于……历经千辛万苦，锡耶拉马德雷的金库就在你面前敞开。马德雷是你的了，你的，你的……"

#: .\spells.json
msgid "friendly hologram activation"
msgstr "友好全息影像激活"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'friendly hologram activation'}
#: .\spells.json
msgid "Activate security hologram."
msgstr "激活安保全息影像。"

#. ~ Message for SPELL '{'str': 'friendly hologram activation'}'
#: .\spells.json
msgid ""
"You activate the Sierra Madre security hologram. Since it is you who's done "
"it, it'll be friendly towards you. The portable emitter's power supply will "
"last only for so long, though."
msgstr "你激活了锡耶拉马德雷安保全息影像。由于是你激活的，它会对你保持友好。不过，便携式发射器的电源只能维持一段时间。"

#: .\spells.json
msgid "stimpack injecting"
msgstr "注射治疗针"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'stimpack injecting'}
#: .\spells.json
msgid "Injecting stimpack"
msgstr "正在注射治疗针"

#. ~ Message for SPELL '{'str': 'stimpack injecting'}'
#: .\spells.json
msgid ""
"You quickly inject stimpack into your body and instantly feel better, just "
"like people in medication ads do."
msgstr "你迅速将治疗针注入体内，立刻感觉好转，就像药品广告里的人一样。"

#: .\spells.json
msgid "Sierra Madre Martini drinking"
msgstr "饮用锡耶拉马德雷马提尼"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Sierra Madre Martini drinking'}
#: .\spells.json
msgid "Drinking Sierra Madre Martini"
msgstr "正在饮用锡耶拉马德雷马提尼"

#. ~ Message for SPELL '{'str': 'Sierra Madre Martini drinking'}'
#: .\spells.json
msgid ""
"You've drunk some Sierra Madre Martini. It doesn't taste very good, but "
"despite being made out of the Cloud, it fills you with strength and power."
msgstr "你喝了一些锡耶拉马德雷马提尼。味道不怎么样，但尽管由云雾制成，它却让你充满力量与活力。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Cloud Kiss intoxication (weak)'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Cloud Kiss intoxication (potent)'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Cloud Kiss intoxication (lethal)'}
#: .\spells.json
msgid "Poisioning with the Cloud"
msgstr "云毒中毒"

#. ~ Message for SPELL '{'str': 'Cloud Kiss intoxication (weak)'}'
#. ~ Message for SPELL '{'str': 'Cloud Kiss intoxication (potent)'}'
#. ~ Message for SPELL '{'str': 'Cloud Kiss intoxication (lethal)'}'
#: .\spells.json
msgid ""
"As you attack your foe, you notice that the Cloud venom starts working..."
msgstr "当你攻击敌人时，你注意到云毒开始生效……"

#: .\items\ammo.json
msgid "microfusion cell"
msgid_plural "microfusion cell"
msgstr[0] "微聚变电池"

#. ~ Description for {'str_sp': 'microfusion cell'}
#: .\items\ammo.json
msgid ""
"Microfusion cell is a new type of energetic ammo developed at Big Mountain "
"research facility to aid US military in the war with China. Excellent power,"
" though the way it works doesn't allow weapons with high rate of fire to "
"utilize it."
msgstr "微聚变电池是巨山研究设施为协助美军对华战争而开发的新型能量弹药。威力卓越，但其工作原理不允许高射速武器使用它。"

#: .\items\ammo.json
msgid "overcharged microfusion cell"
msgid_plural "overcharged microfusion cell"
msgstr[0] "过载微聚变电池"

#. ~ Description for {'str_sp': 'overcharged microfusion cell'}
#: .\items\ammo.json
msgid ""
"Combining a couple of microfusion cells together might yeld one that is more"
" powerful at a cost of it being more prone to misfires."
msgstr "将几个微聚变电池组合在一起可能会产生一个更强大的电池，但代价是更容易发生哑火。"

#: .\items\ammo.json
msgid "energy cell"
msgid_plural "energy cell"
msgstr[0] "能量电池"

#. ~ Description for {'str_sp': 'energy cell'}
#: .\items\ammo.json
msgid ""
"An energy cell, a special ammo type designed for the next-gen laser guns. "
"Essentially a high-capacity battery refitted to be small enough to fit into "
"gun mags."
msgstr "能量电池，一种专为下一代激光枪设计的特殊弹药类型。本质上是一种大容量电池，经过改装后足够小，可以装入枪械弹匣。"

#: .\items\ammo.json
msgid "overcharged energy cell"
msgid_plural "overcharged energy cell"
msgstr[0] "过载能量电池"

#. ~ Description for {'str_sp': 'overcharged energy cell'}
#: .\items\ammo.json
msgid ""
"Combining a couple of energy cells together might yeld one that is more "
"powerful at a cost of it being more prone to misfires."
msgstr "将几个能量电池组合在一起可能会产生一个更强大的电池，但代价是更容易发生哑火。"

#: .\items\ammo.json
msgid "spent microfusion cell"
msgid_plural "spent microfusion cells"
msgstr[0] "耗尽微聚变电池"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'spent microfusion cell'}
#: .\items\ammo.json
msgid "An empty, drained microfusion cell."
msgstr "一个空的、耗尽的微聚变电池。"

#: .\items\ammo.json
msgid "spent energy cell"
msgid_plural "spent energy cells"
msgstr[0] "耗尽能量电池"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'spent energy cell'}
#: .\items\ammo.json
msgid "An empty, drained energy cell."
msgstr "一个空的、耗尽的能量电池。"

#: .\items\ammo.json
msgid "5-cell microfusion pack"
msgid_plural "5-cell microfusion pack"
msgstr[0] "5联装微聚变电池包"

#. ~ Description for {'str_sp': '5-cell microfusion pack'}
#: .\items\ammo.json
msgid ""
"Pack of 5 microfusion cells combined together to satisfy the power "
"requirements of the Gauss rifle."
msgstr "由5个微聚变电池组合而成的电池包，以满足高斯步枪的功率需求。"

#: .\items\ammo.json
msgid "overcharged 5-cell microfusion pack"
msgid_plural "overcharged 5-cell microfusion pack"
msgstr[0] "过载5联装微聚变电池包"

#. ~ Description for {'str_sp': 'overcharged 5-cell microfusion pack'}
#: .\items\ammo.json
msgid ""
"Pack of 5 overcharged microfusion cells combined together to satisfy (and "
"actually exceed at a cost of inferior reliability) the power requirements of"
" the Gauss rifle."
msgstr "由5个过载微聚变电池组合而成的电池包，以满足（实际上以可靠性降低为代价超过了）高斯步枪的功率需求。"

#: .\items\armor.json
msgid "assassin suit"
msgid_plural "assassin suits"
msgstr[0] "刺客套装"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'assassin suit'}
#: .\items\armor.json
msgid ""
"Light, sturdy combat suit designed at Big Mountain research facility. This "
"is the first working prototype of a reverse-engineered Chinese stealth armor"
" used during the war. While nowhere near perfect, it grants its wearer a "
"decent protection for a low encumbrance cost, allowing fast and precise "
"movements. Contains strapped, durable pouch that can store quite a lot of "
"stuff as well as 3 magazine pouches."
msgstr ""
"在巨山研究设施设计的轻便、坚固的战斗服。这是战争期间使用的逆向工程中国潜行装甲的第一个工作原型。虽然远非完美，但它为穿戴者提供了良好的保护，且负重低，允许快速而精确的动作。包含一个绑定的耐用小袋，可以存放大量物品，以及3个弹匣袋。"

#: .\items\armor.json
msgid "Sierra Madre armor"
msgid_plural "Sierra Madre armors"
msgstr[0] "马德雷山脉护甲"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Sierra Madre armor'}
#: .\items\armor.json
msgid ""
"Protective suit worn by the Sierra Madre security personnel. Similar to SWAT"
" armor or riot armor, but lighter. On its back a word \"Security\" is "
"emblazoned with yellow letters."
msgstr "马德雷山脉安保人员穿戴的防护服。类似于SWAT护甲或防暴护甲，但更轻便。其背部用黄色字母印有“Security”字样。"

#: .\items\armor.json
msgid "Sierra Madre security helmet"
msgid_plural "Sierra Madre security helmets"
msgstr[0] "马德雷山脉安保头盔"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Sierra Madre security helmet'}
#: .\items\armor.json
msgid ""
"A black helmet covering the entire head and neck, protecting the wearer from"
" all kinds of damage. Very light for the protection it offers. Originally "
"worn by the Sierra Madre security personnel."
msgstr "覆盖整个头部和颈部的黑色头盔，保护穿戴者免受各种伤害。相对于其提供的防护来说非常轻便。最初由马德雷山脉安保人员穿戴。"

#: .\items\armor.json
msgid "reinforced Sierra Madre armor"
msgid_plural "reinforced Sierra Madre armors"
msgstr[0] "强化马德雷山脉护甲"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'reinforced Sierra Madre armor'}
#: .\items\armor.json
msgid ""
"A reinforced version of the standard Sierra Madre armor, made for the most "
"important guards tasked with protecting the casino itself. On its back a "
"word \"Security\" is emblazoned with yellow letters."
msgstr "标准马德雷山脉护甲的强化版本，专为保护赌场本身的最重要警卫而制作。其背部用黄色字母印有“Security”字样。"

#: .\items\armor.json
msgid "reinforced Sierra Madre security helmet"
msgid_plural "reinforced Sierra Madre security helmets"
msgstr[0] "强化马德雷山脉安保头盔"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'reinforced Sierra Madre security helmet'}
#: .\items\armor.json
msgid ""
"A reinforced version of the standard Sierra Madre security helmet, made for "
"the most important guards tasked with protecting the casino itself."
msgstr "标准马德雷山脉安保头盔的强化版本，专为保护赌场本身的最重要警卫而制作。"

#: .\items\armor.json
msgid "Ghost protective suit"
msgid_plural "Ghost protective suits"
msgstr[0] "幽灵防护服"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Ghost protective suit'}
#: .\items\armor.json
msgid ""
"A type of environmental protection suit worn by the Ghost People. While "
"sturdy and effective, it won't protect from the Cloud. Nothing will. Because"
" Cloud kills fast or slow, gets us ALL."
msgstr "幽灵人穿戴的一种环境防护服。虽然坚固有效，但它无法防护云毒。没有任何东西可以。因为云毒会快或慢地杀死我们，我们所有人。"

#: .\items\books.json
msgid "Dean Domino's journal"
msgid_plural "copies of Dean Domino's journal"
msgstr[0] "迪恩·多米诺的日记"

#. ~ Description for {'str': "Dean Domino's journal", 'str_pl': "copies of
#. Dean Domino's journal"}
#: .\items\books.json
msgid ""
"A perosnal journal of the legendary singer Dean Domino. The last entries "
"contain his story of attempting to rob the Sierra Madre casino vault the "
"night the apocalypse came, then upon failure staying in the villa planning "
"yet another heist attempt while undergoing ghoulification caused by "
"prolonged expousure to the Cloud of toxic gas, finally the story of a "
"mysterious \"Courier\" who once saved Dean's life when together with him "
"(and two other mysterious characters called \"Dog/God\" and Christine) was "
"forced to work for a dangerous, insane man calling himself \"Father Elijah\""
" who also wanted to crack the Sierra Madre Vault open. The most important "
"content of this journal for you is probably the recipe for a special drink, "
"\"Sierra Madre Martini\". According to it, mixing the Cloud residue with "
"common pre-apocalypse junk food in a tin can will change the properties of "
"the toxins to actually strengthen one's body instead of harming it. Also "
"contains some info regarding setting up and disarming traps."
msgstr ""
"传奇歌手迪恩·多米诺的个人日记。最后的条目记载了他在末日降临那晚试图抢劫马德雷赌场金库的故事，失败后留在别墅中计划再次行动，同时因长期暴露在毒云中而逐渐尸鬼化。日记还提到一位神秘的“信使”，曾与迪恩（以及另外两个被称为“狗/神”和克里斯汀的神秘人物）一起被迫为一个自称“以利亚神父”的危险疯子工作，此人同样想打开马德雷金库。这本日记对你最重要的内容可能是特殊饮品“马德雷马提尼”的配方。据记载，将毒云残留物与常见的末日前的垃圾食品在锡罐中混合，会改变毒素的性质，使其强化身体而非造成伤害。此外还包含一些关于设置和拆除陷阱的信息。"

#: .\items\books.json
msgid "Sierra Madre chef's notes"
msgid_plural "copies of Sierra Madre chef's notes"
msgstr[0] "马德雷主厨笔记"

#. ~ Description for {'str': "Sierra Madre chef's notes", 'str_pl': "copies of
#. Sierra Madre chef's notes"}
#: .\items\books.json
msgid ""
"A bunch of notes left by one of the top chiefs working at Sierra Madre. "
"Apart from advanced, elaborate cooking tips and nuances it contains some "
"info of an interesting discovery made by the chief - when he left the cosmic"
" knife on a hotplate for long enough, it warmed up to a very high "
"temperature yet was still comfortable to handle. You could possibly expand "
"the power of cosmic knife further this way, thanks to the wounderful "
"properties of the alloy it's forged from."
msgstr ""
"马德雷赌场一位顶级主厨留下的笔记。除了高级精细的烹饪技巧和细节外，还包含主厨一项有趣发现的信息——当他将宇宙小刀放在电热板上足够长时间后，刀身会升温到极高温度却仍能舒适握持。得益于锻造合金的神奇特性，你或许能以此进一步拓展宇宙小刀的能力。"

#: .\items\books.json
msgid "Father Elijah's notes"
msgid_plural "copies of Father Elijah's notes"
msgstr[0] "以利亚神父的笔记"

#. ~ Description for {'str': "Father Elijah's notes", 'str_pl': "copies of
#. Father Elijah's notes"}
#: .\items\books.json
msgid ""
"A personal journal of Father Elijah. Apart from some rambling about killing "
"every enemy of his own faction to the last man and some psycho's bullshit it"
" contains a vast amount of useful tips about advanced electronics as well as"
" some handy recipes."
msgstr "以利亚神父的个人日记。除了一些关于将自己派系的敌人赶尽杀绝的胡言乱语和疯子的废话外，还包含大量关于高级电子学的实用技巧以及一些便利配方。"

#: .\items\books.json
msgid "Sierra Madre's visitor's journal page"
msgid_plural "Sierra Madre's visitor's journal pages"
msgstr[0] "马德雷访客日记页"

#. ~ Description for {'str': "Sierra Madre's visitor's journal page"}
#: .\items\books.json
msgid ""
"...seems kind enough, signed my poster, and even the promo photo. Kind of a "
"sad look to her, though, like she wasn't really there. And she almost ran "
"when Mr. Domino slipped his arm through hers, and he wasn't even looking at "
"her, like she was a bag hanging on his arm. Something wrong between those "
"two, not sure if Sinclair sees it, but I do."
msgstr ""
"……她看起来挺和善的，给我的海报签了名，甚至还有宣传照。不过她神情有些哀伤，好像心不在焉似的。当多米诺先生把胳膊搭进她臂弯时，她几乎要跑开，而他甚至没看她，仿佛她只是挂在他胳膊上的一个包。这两人之间有点不对劲，不确定辛克莱是否察觉，但我注意到了。"

#: .\items\books.json
msgid "See you in hell asshole"
msgid_plural "See you in hell assholes"
msgstr[0] "地狱见，混蛋"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'See you in hell asshole'}
#: .\items\books.json
msgid ""
"Hope you're about dead when you read this Sierra Madre out of reach Could've"
" had it all, followed that white-arrow-graffiti bastard down here Left those"
" beartraps as presents for you on trail hope you like them shithead Hit my "
"own tripwire you came to take what's mine??? Too bad, I got the last laugh "
"Speakers'll kill you before you get out then we'll settle things in hell "
"Sierra Madre's treasures's mine mine mine"
msgstr ""
"希望你看这封信时快死了 马德雷遥不可及 本可拥有一切 跟着那个白箭头涂鸦的混蛋下来 在沿途留了捕熊夹当礼物给你 希望你喜欢 蠢货 踩中我自己设的绊线 "
"你来抢我的东西？？？ 可惜 最后笑的是我 扬声器会在你逃出去前杀了你 然后我们地狱算账 马德雷的宝藏是我的我的我的"

#: .\items\books.json
msgid "construction worker's stained note"
msgid_plural "construction worker's stained notes"
msgstr[0] "建筑工人的污渍笔记"

#. ~ Description for {'str': "construction worker's stained note"}
#: .\items\books.json
msgid ""
"Not going to rat me out for what happened in the Villa. I'm not the one who "
"laid the foundation, and I'm not going to take the fall for the supports, "
"either. They try and pin this on me, I'll let them all know what's really "
"going on with the construction contracts."
msgstr "别想因为别墅里的事出卖我。地基不是我打的，支撑结构出问题也别想让我背锅。他们要是想栽赃给我，我就把建筑合同里的猫腻全抖出来。"

#: .\items\books.json
msgid "Sierra Madre toxic gas note"
msgid_plural "Sierra Madre toxic gas notes"
msgstr[0] "马德雷毒气记录"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Sierra Madre toxic gas note'}
#: .\items\books.json
msgid ""
"A note about the Sierra Madre toxic gas building up in the ventilation "
"system hurting three construction workers. Apparently they had no idea from "
"where it came from either."
msgstr "一份关于马德雷毒气在通风系统中积聚导致三名建筑工人受伤的记录。显然他们也不清楚毒气来源。"

#: .\items\books.json
msgid "Vera Keyes' insomnia"
msgid_plural "Vera Keyes' insomnias"
msgstr[0] "薇拉·凯斯的失眠症"

#. ~ Description for {'str': "Vera Keyes' insomnia"}
#: .\items\books.json
msgid ""
"A note about Vera Keyes' health condition mentioning severe insomnia. "
"Apparently the autodocs at the clinic were capable of alleviating its "
"effects."
msgstr "关于薇拉·凯斯健康状况的笔记，提到严重失眠症。显然诊所的自动医疗机能够缓解其症状。"

#: .\items\books.json
msgid "guard's commentary about the prohibtion"
msgid_plural "guard's commentary about the prohibtions"
msgstr[0] "警卫关于禁令的评论"

#. ~ Description for {'str': "guard's commentary about the prohibtion"}
#: .\items\books.json
msgid ""
"Sinclair's prohibition list is going to be difficult to enforce and told him"
" so. He claims we're getting an automated system that would confiscate items"
" even the slightest bit radioactive or foreign and ship them back to the "
"visitor's source address. Asked about items already in the Villa (didn't "
"mention the construction crew) and he dismissed it. Of course, no sooner "
"than Sinclair gives his prohibition speech, his pal swings by the same hour,"
" asking how \"hardnosed\" we were going to be. Told me he couldn't guarantee"
" he could keep me supplied if I didn't treat his \"friends\" with the same "
"respect. Prick."
msgstr ""
"辛克莱的违禁品清单执行起来会很困难，我也这么告诉过他。他声称我们会安装自动系统，能没收任何带微量放射性或外来物品并寄回访客来源地址。我问起别墅里已有的物品（没提建筑队），他直接搪塞过去。当然，辛克莱刚发布禁令讲话，他那朋友就同一时间跑来，问我们执行会有多“严格”。告诉我如果我不以同等尊重对待他的“朋友”，就不能保证继续给我供货。混账东西。"

#: .\items\books.json
msgid "guard's commentary about the prohibtion enforcement difficulties"
msgid_plural ""
"guard's commentary about the prohibtion enforcement difficultiess"
msgstr[0] "警卫关于禁令执行困难的评论"

#. ~ Description for {'str': "guard's commentary about the prohibtion
#. enforcement difficulties"}
#: .\items\books.json
msgid ""
"After another \"discussion\" with the Puesta del Sol crew, told Chief it'd "
"be difficult to enforce the prohibition list, let alone the searches. Chief "
"had the Gala on his brain, said Sinclair put construction of the Villa more "
"important than patting down the construction crews for liquor and chems as "
"long as they didn't hurt anyone or each other. Got a little hot under the "
"collar, Chief did too, told me to walk it off. This whole thing stinks. "
"Chief's barely got time for me, now Sinclair's turning a blind eye to things"
" in the Villa because his friend's running the show?"
msgstr ""
"又和普埃斯塔德索尔施工队“讨论”后，我告诉警长执行违禁品清单会很困难，更不用说搜身了。警长满脑子都是开业庆典，说辛克莱认为别墅建设比搜查建筑队携带的酒类和药物更重要——只要他们不伤害他人或彼此。我有点上火，警长也是，让我出去冷静下。整件事都透着不对劲。警长几乎没时间管我，现在辛克莱对别墅里的事睁只眼闭只眼，就因为是他朋友在管事？"

#: .\items\books.json
msgid "driving ban order"
msgid_plural "driving ban orders"
msgstr[0] "禁驾令"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'driving ban order'}
#: .\items\books.json
msgid ""
"An order detailing the ban on driving in Sierra Madre as well as the "
"construction of the streets preventing usage of vehicles."
msgstr "一份详细规定马德雷地区禁止驾驶以及道路设计阻止车辆通行的命令。"

#: .\items\books.json
msgid "new security info"
msgid_plural "new security infos"
msgstr[0] "新安保信息"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'new security info'}
#: .\items\books.json
msgid ""
"A note about the security rules enforced in the Sierra Madre by it's founder"
" Sinclair. Apparently any potentially dangerous item of the foreign origin "
"had to be confiscated and the security personnel had to take notes about who"
" enters and who leaves."
msgstr "关于马德雷创始人辛克莱实施的安保规则的记录。显然任何可能危险的外来物品都必须没收，安保人员必须记录进出人员信息。"

#: .\items\books.json
msgid "communication system setup"
msgid_plural "communication system setups"
msgstr[0] "通讯系统设置"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'communication system setup'}
#: .\items\books.json
msgid ""
"According to what's written on this page, guards stationed at the police "
"station prepared an entire broadcast system so that they could watch the "
"Sierra Madre Opening Gala show on their shift."
msgstr "根据这页记录，驻守警察局的警卫搭建了完整的广播系统，以便在值班时观看马德雷开业庆典演出。"

#: .\items\books.json
msgid "Sinclair's visit report"
msgid_plural "Sinclair's visit reports"
msgstr[0] "辛克莱视察报告"

#. ~ Description for {'str': "Sinclair's visit report"}
#: .\items\books.json
msgid "A note about the control visit of Sinclair."
msgstr "关于辛克莱控制视察的记录。"

#: .\items\books.json
msgid "weapon transfer list"
msgid_plural "weapon transfer lists"
msgstr[0] "武器移交清单"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'weapon transfer list'}
#: .\items\books.json
msgid ""
"This list details all the guns, ammo and explosives Sierra Madre guards "
"received."
msgstr "这份清单详细列出了马德雷警卫接收的所有枪支、弹药和爆炸物。"

#: .\items\books.json
msgid "guard's comment on vending machines"
msgid_plural "guard's comment on vending machiness"
msgstr[0] "守卫对自动售货机的评论"

#. ~ Description for {'str': "guard's comment on vending machines"}
#: .\items\books.json
msgid ""
"A note about the Sierra Madre vending machines selling commodities for "
"casino chips, but in case of an emergency capable of dispensing military and"
" medical supplies as well."
msgstr "关于马德雷山脉自动售货机用赌场筹码出售商品的说明，但在紧急情况下也能分发军事和医疗物资。"

#: .\items\books.json
msgid "ventilation system report"
msgid_plural "ventilation system reports"
msgstr[0] "通风系统报告"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'ventilation system report'}
#: .\items\books.json
msgid ""
"A report about the Sierra Madre ventilation system failing and spitting out "
"some sort of toxic gas, the same one you're breathing like now. Seems like "
"even Sinclair himself had no idea what it was and where it came from... Some"
" technicians working on the system have been rendered unconscious by the gas"
" despite wearing protection suits. Makes you feel better about not having "
"one anyway... Especially given how the gas eroded the suits' locks, trapping"
" the wearers inside. To this day they still roam the streets of Sierra "
"Madre, trapped in their suits, jealous of everything that lives..."
msgstr ""
"一份关于马德雷山脉通风系统故障并喷出某种有毒气体的报告，就是你此刻呼吸的那种。看来连辛克莱本人也不知道那是什么、从何而来……一些穿着防护服检修系统的技术人员被气体熏晕了。这让你觉得没穿防护服反而更好……尤其是考虑到气体腐蚀了防护服的锁扣，把穿着者困在里面。至今他们仍游荡在马德雷山脉的街道上，困在防护服里，嫉妒着一切活物……"

#: .\items\books.json
msgid "construction status report"
msgid_plural "construction status reports"
msgstr[0] "施工状态报告"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'construction status report'}
#: .\items\books.json
msgid ""
"...the Villa's like cardboard, but the casino? That place isn't built for "
"people to just gamble, it's a place for them to take cover if the big ones "
"hit. Those doors can be hermetically sealed, and whatever they got lining "
"the floors screws up anything not hooked up direct by wires. Word is, while "
"Mr. Yesterday got the Villa covered, Sinclair's locking up the Sierra Madre "
"like a golden trap."
msgstr ""
"……别墅区像纸糊的，但赌场呢？那地方可不是让人随便赌博的，而是万一发生大灾难时供人避难的地方。那些门可以完全密封，地板下的特殊材料会干扰任何非直接有线连接的设备。有传言说，虽然耶斯特戴先生负责别墅区，但辛克莱把马德雷山脉锁得像一个黄金陷阱。"

#: .\items\books.json
msgid "Sierra Madre infrastructure commentary note"
msgid_plural "Sierra Madre infrastructure commentary notes"
msgstr[0] "马德雷山脉基础设施评论笔记"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Sierra Madre infrastructure commentary note'}
#: .\items\books.json
msgid ""
"As shoddy as the support beams are for most of these buildings, the "
"ventilation system's worse, and the problems they had over at Puesta... "
"sure, when you count our bonuses, it's good, but not when the workers are "
"coughing to death. Hate to see what this place spits out if someone let the "
"ventilation system chug along for a few years, we'd have another Greener "
"Pastures on our hand, easy, and a pile of bodies beyond it."
msgstr ""
"这些建筑的大部分支撑梁已经够糟糕了，通风系统更差，普埃斯塔那边的问题……当然，算上我们的奖金，这工作还不错，但工人们咳得要死的时候就不是了。真不敢想象如果让通风系统再运转几年，这地方会喷出什么来，我们手上肯定会多一个“更绿的牧场”，轻而易举，后面还会堆满尸体。"

#: .\items\books.json
msgid "dishonest worker's inner reports"
msgid_plural "dishonest worker's inner reportss"
msgstr[0] "不诚实工人的内部报告"

#. ~ Description for {'str': "dishonest worker's inner reports"}
#: .\items\books.json
msgid ""
"Some casual reports detailing the dishonest practices of part of the villa "
"construction crew mixed together with complaints about missing essential "
"shipments."
msgstr "一些随意报告，详细描述了部分别墅施工队的不诚实行为，并夹杂着对缺失重要物资运输的抱怨。"

#: .\items\books.json
msgid "doctor's note"
msgid_plural "doctor's notes"
msgstr[0] "医生笔记"

#. ~ Description for {'str': "doctor's note"}
#: .\items\books.json
msgid ""
"Ms Keyes showed up today (sans Sinclair), escorted by Mr. Domino. He "
"explained to me Ms Keyes had developed a throat infection, and asked if the "
"Auto-Doc could help. I asked about the Sierra Madre's Auto-Doc. He said he "
"didn't want to \"alarm\" Sinclair. Ran some tests. Ms Keyes' voice is fine, "
"her loss of voice was more listlessness, symptomatic of excessive Med-X "
"usage. When I tried to speak to her about it, Mr. Domino intervened. I "
"warned them too much of the Chem could render a subject comatose, and Domino"
" laughed. I lost my temper, and he said they'd return another time when I "
"was in \"better spirits.\" Despise that man."
msgstr ""
"凯斯女士今天来了（辛克莱没来），由多米诺先生陪同。他向我解释说凯斯女士喉咙感染了，问自动医疗机是否能帮忙。我问了马德雷山脉的自动医疗机。他说他不想“惊动”辛克莱。做了一些检查。凯斯女士的嗓音没问题，她失声更多是倦怠的表现，是过度使用Med-"
"X的症状。当我试图和她谈这件事时，多米诺先生插话了。我警告他们这种化学药剂用太多会导致昏迷，多米诺笑了。我发了脾气，他说等我“心情好点”他们再来。真讨厌那个人。"

#: .\items\books.json
msgid "chief physician's note"
msgid_plural "chief physician's notes"
msgstr[0] "主治医生笔记"

#. ~ Description for {'str': "chief physician's note"}
#: .\items\books.json
msgid ""
"Domino stopped by to ask about the test results and Vera's voice. He seemed "
"concerned she would lose her voice for the Gala Event. I told him if Ms "
"Keyes was concerned, she should see me, and I would only disclose any "
"medical information to her. I told him the Auto-Docs were more than capable "
"of healing Ms Keyes voice if she developed any throat infection, and we "
"could even operate if need be if she tore her larynx. He seemed satisfied by"
" the news, apologized, amazingly enough, and left a bottle of wine as a "
"token of his appreciation. I told him I felt it was inappropriate, he "
"insisted. I dumped it in the trash."
msgstr ""
"多米诺顺道来询问检查结果和薇拉的声音。他似乎担心她会在庆典活动上失声。我告诉他，如果凯斯女士担心，她应该来见我，而且我只向她本人透露任何医疗信息。我告诉他，如果凯斯女士喉咙感染，自动医疗机完全有能力治好她的声音，如果她撕裂了声带，我们甚至可以在必要时进行手术。他听到这个消息似乎很满意，道了歉，令人惊讶的是，还留下一瓶酒作为感谢。我告诉他我觉得这不合适，他坚持要送。我把它倒进了垃圾桶。"

#: .\items\books.json
msgid "gas incident medical report"
msgid_plural "gas incident medical reports"
msgstr[0] "毒气事件医疗报告"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'gas incident medical report'}
#: .\items\books.json
msgid ""
"A detailed medical report about the toxic gas incident and the patients "
"exposed to it. The doctors in the clinic had no idea what it was as well, "
"despite having access to a very advanced medical equipment."
msgstr "一份关于有毒气体事件及暴露患者的详细医疗报告。诊所的医生们尽管拥有非常先进的医疗设备，也不知道那是什么。"

#: .\items\books.json
msgid "Vera Keyes' partitures"
msgid_plural "Vera Keyes' partituress"
msgstr[0] "薇拉·凯斯的乐谱"

#. ~ Description for {'str': "Vera Keyes' partitures"}
#: .\items\books.json
msgid ""
"Partitures belonging to Vera Keyes', meant to be used by her during her "
"performance."
msgstr "属于薇拉·凯斯的乐谱，供她演出时使用。"

#: .\items\books.json
msgid "bar incident log"
msgid_plural "bar incident logs"
msgstr[0] "酒吧事件记录"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'bar incident log'}
#: .\items\books.json
msgid ""
"Complaint: Mrs. Purvis/Drunk and Disorderly Sierra Madre Security Log: "
"11:02PM Guard on Call: Morris, Tyler Describe the Incident: 10PM, received "
"complaints about noise in upper bar, then emergency call from the an floor "
"cashier cage who reported (quote) \"old bat on ceiling.\" Investigating, "
"found guests cheering Mrs. Millicent Purvis, 72, who had climbed over the "
"upper bar railing and was walking on the support beams, indicating loudly "
"that she was (quote), \"going to join the circus.\" She had already tripped "
"over one Holo-Emitter (unhurt), and was inviting guests out on the beams so "
"we could \"use them like monkey bars.\" Climbed after her, cornered her near"
" the rafter over the cashier's area, then brought Mrs. Purvis to holding and"
" called her daughter to come escort her to her room. No damage done to "
"rafters or the emitter. Mrs. Purvis's daughter was visibly agitated by the "
"incident and too embarrassed to take any legal action saying that she "
"(quote), \"didn't want to cause any more trouble for Mr. Sinclair.\" Need to"
" gate off the rafter area to prevent repeat incidents."
msgstr ""
"投诉：珀维斯夫人/醉酒闹事 马德雷山脉安全日志：晚上11:02 值班警卫：莫里斯，泰勒 "
"事件描述：晚上10点，接到上层酒吧噪音投诉，随后接到楼层收银笼的紧急呼叫，报告（引述）“天花板上有只老蝙蝠”。调查发现，客人们正在为72岁的米莉森特·珀维斯夫人欢呼，她爬过了上层酒吧栏杆，走在支撑梁上，大声表示她（引述）“要去加入马戏团”。她已经绊倒了一个全息发射器（未受伤），并邀请客人到梁上，这样我们就能“把它们当单杠用”。爬上去追她，在收银区附近的椽子上截住了她，然后将珀维斯夫人带到拘留室，并打电话叫她女儿来护送她回房间。椽子或发射器没有损坏。珀维斯夫人的女儿对此事明显感到不安，并且太尴尬而不愿采取任何法律行动，说她（引述）“不想给辛克莱先生添更多麻烦”。需要封锁椽子区域以防止类似事件再次发生。"

#: .\items\books.json
msgid "bar incident log, part 2"
msgid_plural "bar incident log, part 2s"
msgstr[0] "酒吧事件记录，第二部分"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'bar incident log, part 2'}
#: .\items\books.json
msgid ""
"Complaint: Lost and Found Sierra Madre Security Log: 8:07AM Guard on Call: "
"Morris, Tyler Describe the Incident: Mrs. Purvis daughter called down to ask"
" if we happened to find her mother's purse, which she may have dropped "
"during last night's \"stroll.\" We found the purse on the main floor. None "
"of the valuables were inside, may have been taken when the purse dropped, or"
" Mrs. Purvis may have emptied the purse contents during last night's "
"incident."
msgstr ""
"投诉：失物招领 马德雷山脉安全日志：上午8:07 值班警卫：莫里斯，泰勒 "
"事件描述：珀维斯夫人的女儿打电话来问我们是否碰巧找到了她母亲的手提包，可能是昨晚“散步”时掉的。我们在主楼层找到了手提包。里面没有贵重物品，可能是在包掉的时候被拿走了，或者珀维斯夫人可能在昨晚的事件中清空了包里的东西。"

#: .\items\books.json
msgid "security measure meeting note"
msgid_plural "security measure meeting notes"
msgstr[0] "安全措施会议记录"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'security measure meeting note'}
#: .\items\books.json
msgid ""
"Since you missed it, Sinclair outlined security measures today. Wasn't blind"
" to what was happening in the news, wanted to take steps if the Chinese got "
"a foothold on American soil. Ran us through the added functionality of the "
"holograms, then explained the construction of the casino, its emergency "
"protocols, and the broadcast signal we're using for the Gala Event. Guy's a "
"nut job, still, seems to have the bases covered. Guess the isolation of the "
"casino was intentional. Not sure what he's hoping to protect, sure seems "
"obsessed with it."
msgstr ""
"既然你错过了，辛克莱今天概述了安全措施。他并非对新闻中发生的事情视而不见，如果中国人在美国土地上站稳脚跟，他想采取措施。他向我们介绍了全息影像的附加功能，然后解释了赌场的结构、应急协议，以及我们用于庆典活动的广播信号。这家伙是个疯子，不过，似乎考虑得很周全。我猜赌场的隔离是故意的。不确定他想保护什么，但肯定对此很着迷。"

#: .\items\books.json
msgid "emergency protocols"
msgid_plural "emergency protocolss"
msgstr[0] "应急协议"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'emergency protocols'}
#: .\items\books.json
msgid ""
"Been reading this over: \"In the event of a fire, chemical leak, nuclear "
"attack, or other threat to the casino, the interior and exterior doors will "
"hermetically seal to prevent harm coming to the guests. During this time, "
"Holograms will be deployed and assume threat status until the lockdown is "
"ended.\" Guess you can't be too careful these days. Still, what if there was"
" another leak at the switching station? Not to mention the gas valves in the"
" kitchen. If those got hit, the casino's a torch."
msgstr ""
"一直在读这个：“在发生火灾、化学品泄漏、核攻击或其他对赌场的威胁时，内外门将完全密封，以防止客人受到伤害。在此期间，全息影像将被部署并进入威胁状态，直到封锁结束。”"
" 我想这年头再怎么小心也不为过。不过，如果交换站再次泄漏怎么办？更不用说厨房里的燃气阀门了。如果那些被击中，赌场就是个火炬。"

#: .\items\books.json
msgid "note on hologram security system"
msgid_plural "note on hologram security systems"
msgstr[0] "关于全息影像安全系统的说明"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'note on hologram security system'}
#: .\items\books.json
msgid ""
"A brief explanation about the Sierra Madre holographic security system "
"paired with a warning to not touch or try to disable hologram emitters."
msgstr "关于马德雷山脉全息影像安全系统的简要说明，并附有警告：不要触摸或试图禁用全息影像发射器。"

#: .\items\books.json
msgid "Tampico's show list"
msgid_plural "Tampico's show lists"
msgstr[0] "坦皮科的演出名单"

#. ~ Description for {'str': "Tampico's show list"}
#: .\items\books.json
msgid ""
"The Sierra Madre opens its doors to the world! The opening of our great "
"Casino & Resort will feature a unique Gala, showcasing artists of world-"
"renown! Miss Vera Keyes. Mr. Dean Domino. Joey Baxter. And, Wilfred the "
"Wizard. Come join us at the grandest event in the history of the West. We "
"welcome you to the best time of your life! Sincerely, The Sierra Madre's "
"Management."
msgstr ""
"马德雷山脉向世界敞开大门！我们伟大的赌场度假村开业将举办一场独特的庆典，展示世界知名的艺术家！薇拉·凯斯小姐。迪恩·多米诺先生。乔伊·巴克斯特。以及，巫师威尔弗雷德。来加入我们，参加西部历史上最盛大的活动。我们欢迎您度过一生中最美好的时光！诚挚地，马德雷山脉管理层。"

#: .\items\books.json
msgid "message for Mrs E. Sainz"
msgid_plural "message for Mrs E. Sainzs"
msgstr[0] "给E·赛恩斯夫人的留言"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'message for Mrs E. Sainz'}
#: .\items\books.json
msgid ""
"I'm on my way! I'll be right there, Eve! Just hide until I get there. Do "
"whatever you need to, understand!? I'm not going to let anything happen to "
"you."
msgstr "我这就来！我马上到，伊芙！先躲好等我。做你该做的事，明白吗！？我绝不会让你出事的。"

#: .\items\books.json
msgid "message for Mr J. Lester"
msgid_plural "message for Mr J. Lesters"
msgstr[0] "给J·莱斯特先生的留言"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'message for Mr J. Lester'}
#: .\items\books.json
msgid ""
"John, help! Everything exploded! There's smoke. Holograms are firing at "
"people! We can't get out, John! Please!"
msgstr "约翰，救命！全炸了！到处都是烟。全息影像在朝人开枪！我们出不去了，约翰！求你了！"

#: .\items\books.json
msgid "commentary about the shipments of cosmic knives"
msgid_plural "commentary about the shipments of cosmic knivess"
msgstr[0] "关于宇宙餐刀货运的评论"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'commentary about the shipments of cosmic
#. knives'}
#: .\items\books.json
msgid ""
"Another (!) shipment of kitchen knives for the Cantina Madrid came in today,"
" with their new \"space age\" alloy polymer material. We've got way more "
"than we need for the Gala Event, even if everyone had 3 steak knives! But "
"it's always the best for Sinclair, always, always, always, always, he "
"insists everything must be perfect. These knives are sharp, too sharp! One "
"of the chefs almost lost their thumb when dicing vegetables, and were losing"
" cutting boards at the rate of at least one per day. The knives just slice "
"right through them! Running out of dishrags to mop up the blood."
msgstr ""
"马德里小酒馆今天又（！）到了一批厨房餐刀，用的是那种新型“太空时代”合金聚合物材料。就算晚宴上每人用三把牛排刀，我们也远远超量了！但辛克莱总是要求最好、最好、最好、最好，他坚持一切必须完美。这些刀太锋利了，锋利过头！有个厨师切菜时差点把拇指切掉，砧板也以每天至少一块的速度报废——刀直接就能劈穿它们！擦血的抹布都快不够用了。"

#: .\items\books.json
msgid "Dog command tape"
msgid_plural "Dog command tapes"
msgstr[0] "犬类指令磁带"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Dog command tape'}
#: .\items\books.json
msgid "A holotape with pre-recorded message saying: \"Dog, back in the cage\"."
msgstr "一段预录了“狗，回笼子去”信息的全息磁带。"

#: .\items\books.json
msgid "Dean Domino's blackmail evidence"
msgid_plural "Dean Domino's blackmail evidences"
msgstr[0] "迪恩·多米诺的勒索证据"

#. ~ Description for {'str': "Dean Domino's blackmail evidence"}
#: .\items\books.json
msgid ""
"A holotape containing the recorded dialogue between Vera and Dean in which "
"Dean threatens to reveal Vera's Med-X addiction if she refuses to do as he "
"says."
msgstr "一段全息磁带，内含薇拉与迪恩的对话录音，其中迪恩威胁若薇拉不按他说的做，就揭发她对Med-X（医疗X）的上瘾。"

#: .\items\books.json
msgid "Dean Domino \"Saw Her yesterday\""
msgid_plural "Dean Domino \"Saw Her yesterday\"s"
msgstr[0] "迪恩·多米诺《昨日见她》"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Dean Domino "Saw Her yesterday"'}
#: .\items\books.json
msgid ""
"A holotape containing recording of a Dean Domino's song \"Saw Her "
"yesterday\"."
msgstr "一段全息磁带，内含迪恩·多米诺的歌曲《昨日见她》的录音。"

#: .\items\books.json
msgid "Vera Keyes \"Let the Bright Tomorrow in\""
msgid_plural "Vera Keyes \"Let the Bright Tomorrow in\"s"
msgstr[0] "薇拉·凯斯《让光明明日来临》"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Vera Keyes "Let the Bright Tomorrow in"'}
#: .\items\books.json
msgid ""
"A holotape containing recording of a Vera Keyes' song \"Let the Bright "
"Tomorrow in\". Can be used with the other songs to get a combination of "
"Vera's voice."
msgstr "一段全息磁带，内含薇拉·凯斯的歌曲《让光明明日来临》的录音。可与其他歌曲组合使用，以合成薇拉的嗓音。"

#: .\items\books.json
msgid "Vera Keyes \"Go to the Faraway\""
msgid_plural "Vera Keyes \"Go to the Faraway\"s"
msgstr[0] "薇拉·凯斯《前往远方》"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Vera Keyes "Go to the Faraway"'}
#: .\items\books.json
msgid ""
"A holotape containing recording of a Vera Keyes' song \"Go to the Faraway\"."
" Can be used with the other songs to get a combination of Vera's voice."
msgstr "一段全息磁带，内含薇拉·凯斯的歌曲《前往远方》的录音。可与其他歌曲组合使用，以合成薇拉的嗓音。"

#: .\items\books.json
msgid "Vera Keyes \"Begin Again\""
msgid_plural "Vera Keyes \"Begin Again\"s"
msgstr[0] "薇拉·凯斯《重新开始》"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Vera Keyes "Begin Again"'}
#: .\items\books.json
msgid ""
"A holotape containing recording of a Vera Keyes' song \"Begin Again\". Can "
"be used with the other songs to get a combination of Vera's voice."
msgstr "一段全息磁带，内含薇拉·凯斯的歌曲《重新开始》的录音。可与其他歌曲组合使用，以合成薇拉的嗓音。"

#: .\items\books.json
msgid "Vera Keyes' audition recording"
msgid_plural "Vera Keyes' audition recordings"
msgstr[0] "薇拉·凯斯的试镜录音"

#. ~ Description for {'str': "Vera Keyes' audition recording"}
#: .\items\books.json
msgid ""
"A holotape containing recording of a Vera Keyes' audition for the movie "
"\"Love Sets Sail!\" Turns out she was rather a bad actress, after all. Just "
"like the movies she played in."
msgstr "一段全息磁带，内含薇拉·凯斯为电影《爱启航！》试镜的录音。结果证明她演技实在不怎么样，就跟她演的那些电影一样。"

#: .\items\books.json
msgid "Sierra Madre Vault worker's note"
msgid_plural "Sierra Madre Vault worker's notes"
msgstr[0] "马德雷山金库工人的笔记"

#. ~ Description for {'str': "Sierra Madre Vault worker's note"}
#: .\items\books.json
msgid ""
"This job doesn't pay enough, working down here with those walking lightshows"
" gets on my nerves. And the elevator... does Sinclair know how dangerous it "
"is to have the elevator lock like that? If someone accidentally trips the "
"deadman's switch inside his Vault... even Sinclair himself... this whole "
"place becomes a big metal coffin. Lou tried to tell him and Sinclair said it"
" would be \"user error.\""
msgstr ""
"这活儿给的钱不够，在下面跟那些走来走去的灯光秀（全息警卫）一起工作真让人神经紧张。还有电梯……辛克莱知道把电梯锁成那样有多危险吗？要是有人在金库里不小心触发了死人开关……就算是辛克莱自己……这整个地方就会变成一口大金属棺材。卢试着提醒过他，辛克莱却说那会是“用户操作失误”。"

#: .\items\books.json
msgid "note about turrets in the vault"
msgid_plural "note about turrets in the vaults"
msgstr[0] "关于金库内炮塔的笔记"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'note about turrets in the vault'}
#: .\items\books.json
msgid ""
"Don't use this unless strictly necessary. The Vault is off-limits. There is "
"no reason to enter it unless your clearance is personally approved by Mr. "
"Sinclair. Still, if anything were to go wrong with those security systems, "
"use this password in the Turret-Defense terminal inside the Vault's Chamber:"
" \"HeartArrow\". Lou Martin, M&M Construction Inc. Crew Chief."
msgstr ""
"非绝对必要切勿使用。金库为禁区。除非获得辛克莱先生亲自批准，否则严禁进入。但万一那些安保系统出问题，可在金库室内的炮塔防御终端使用此密码：“HeartArrow”。卢·马丁，M&M建筑公司，工头。"

#: .\items\books.json
msgid "extracted holotape"
msgid_plural "extracted holotapes"
msgstr[0] "提取的全息磁带"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'extracted holotape'}
#: .\items\books.json
msgid ""
"Vera, If you're reading this, I know what you and Dean had planned tonight "
"on the eve of the Gala Event. I loved you very much, and whatever possessed "
"you to choose Dean's arm over my hand is beyond me. Whether it was greed or "
"lust, it has led you here and will forever keep us apart. I hope it leaves "
"you as empty as you left me. As much as you sought what was inside the "
"Sierra Madre, now it will keep you. The door has sealed, the elevator has "
"left, and not even your voice will unlock it. This casino was my gift to "
"you, and you now will be its heart for all time. Sincerely, Frederick "
"Sinclair"
msgstr ""
"薇拉，如果你读到这个，我知道你和迪恩在晚宴前夜计划了什么。我曾深爱你，你究竟为何选择迪恩的臂膀而非我的手，我无法理解。无论是贪婪还是欲望，都将你引至此地，并让我们永远分离。我希望它让你感到空虚，正如你留给我的那样。你如此渴望马德雷山内的东西，现在它将永远困住你。门已封死，电梯已离去，连你的声音也无法开启它。这座赌场曾是我给你的礼物，如今你将永远成为它的心脏。诚挚的，弗雷德里克·辛克莱"

#: .\items\books.json
