"A tainted flesh of Sierra Madre Ghost People. Despite being dried, it still "
"looks poisonous."
msgstr "Sierra Madre 幽灵人的受污染肉体。尽管干制了，它看起来仍然有毒。"

#: .\items\consumables.json
msgid "Sierra Madre Martini"
msgid_plural "Sierra Madre Martini"
msgstr[0] "Sierra Madre 马提尼"

#. ~ Description for {'str_sp': 'Sierra Madre Martini'}
#: .\items\consumables.json
msgid ""
"Concentrated, solidified Sierra Madre toxins mixed in a tin can with some "
"junk food. While still unhealthy, apparently a right combination of "
"chemicals found in pre-apocalypse junk food is able to change the properties"
" of the toxic gas to actually aid you, not hurt you. You can't wrap your "
"head around it, but hey, it works! Beware of drinking too much though - it's"
" addictive."
msgstr ""
"浓缩、固化的 Sierra Madre "
"毒素与一些垃圾食品混合在一个锡罐中。虽然仍然不健康，但显然，末日前的垃圾食品中某些化学物质的正确组合能够改变有毒气体的性质，使其实际上帮助你，而不是伤害你。你无法理解，但嘿，它有效！不过要小心别喝太多——它会让人上瘾。"

#: .\items\consumables.json
msgid "stimpack"
msgid_plural "stimpack"
msgstr[0] "治疗针"

#. ~ Description for {'str_sp': 'stimpack'}
#: .\items\consumables.json
msgid ""
"A syringe filled with a strange, dense, light-red substance, serving as a "
"state-of-tech emergency medical aid. Once injected, it boosts tissue "
"regeneration, blood pumping, adrenaline pumping, breathing and thinking "
"rapidly, making one feel refreshed and healing a lot of abuse."
msgstr ""
"一支装满奇异、浓稠、浅红色物质的注射器，作为高科技紧急医疗援助。注射后能促进组织再生、加速血液循环、激发肾上腺素、提升呼吸与思维速度，使人精神焕发并治愈大量损伤。"

#: .\items\consumables.json
msgid "Mentats"
msgid_plural "Mentats"
msgstr[0] "曼他特"

#. ~ Use action activation_message for {'str_sp': 'Mentats'}.
#: .\items\consumables.json
msgid "You take some Mentats pills."
msgstr "你服用了一些曼他特药片。"

#. ~ Description for {'str_sp': 'Mentats'}
#: .\items\consumables.json
msgid ""
"Red pills developed by Med-Tek. No, they will not make you see the truth "
"behind this insane, cruel world... Wait, they actually might do, since they "
"are designed to temporairly boost perception and intelligence. Overdose can "
"be fatal and addictive, though - beware of uncovering more truth that you "
"can handle..."
msgstr ""
"由Med-"
"Tek研发的红色药片。不，它们不会让你看透这个疯狂残酷世界的真相……等等，或许真的可以，因为它们旨在暂时提升感知力和智力。但过量服用可能致命并导致成瘾——小心发掘出超出你承受能力的真相……"

#: .\items\consumables.json
msgid "Med-X"
msgid_plural "Med-X"
msgstr[0] "Med-X"

#. ~ Use action activation_message for {'str_sp': 'Med-X'}.
#: .\items\consumables.json
msgid "You inject a dose of Med-X."
msgstr "你注射了一剂Med-X。"

#. ~ Description for {'str_sp': 'Med-X'}
#: .\items\consumables.json
msgid ""
"A highly effective painkiller that also boosts body regeneration "
"capabilities. Has lower chance of overdose than conventional painkillers, "
"but still can make you addicted or straight-up kill you."
msgstr "一种高效止痛药，同时能增强身体再生能力。比传统止痛药过量风险更低，但仍可能致瘾或直接致命。"

#: .\items\consumables.json
msgid "Stealth Boy"
msgid_plural "Stealth Boys"
msgstr[0] "潜行小子"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Stealth Boy'}
#: .\items\consumables.json
msgid ""
"A high-tech device that generates a sophisticated field around the user that"
" deflects and curves light beams in a way that looking at it an observer "
"would see what's behind the user, effectively granting invisibility. Sadly "
"it's a single use item and can't be recharged in any way after it uses up "
"all its power supply. Brought to you by Big Mountain research facility."
msgstr ""
"一种高科技设备，能在使用者周围生成精密力场，偏转并弯曲光线，使观察者看到使用者背后的景象，从而实现隐形。可惜这是单次使用物品，电力耗尽后无法以任何方式充电。由大山脉研究设施提供。"

#: .\items\consumables.json
msgid "portable security hologram emitter"
msgid_plural "portable security hologram emitters"
msgstr[0] "便携式安保全息发射器"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'portable security hologram emitter'}
#: .\items\consumables.json
msgid ""
"A portable version of the Sierra Madre security hologram emitter, allowing "
"you to place a friendly holo guard of your own. One-time use only, and it "
"has only so much power stored allowing the activated hologram to exist for "
"only so long."
msgstr "锡耶拉马德雷安保全息发射器的便携版本，允许你部署一个友方全息守卫。仅限单次使用，且储存能量有限，激活的全息影像仅能存在一段时间。"

#: .\items\gunmods.json
msgid "Holorifle scope"
msgid_plural "Holorifle scopes"
msgstr[0] "全息步枪瞄准镜"

#: .\items\gunmods.json
msgid ""
"A 2.86x scope designed specifically for the holorifle. Has a nice circle-"
"shaped, black crosshair clearly visible on slightly greenish lens."
msgstr "专为全息步枪设计的2.86倍瞄准镜。带有清晰的圆形黑色十字准线，在微泛绿色的镜片上清晰可见。"

#: .\items\gunmods.json
msgid "sights"
msgstr "瞄准具"

#: .\items\gunmods.json
msgctxt "gun_type_type"
msgid "holorifle"
msgstr "全息步枪"

#: .\items\gunmods.json
msgid "Holorifle focus optics"
msgid_plural "Holorifle focus optics"
msgstr[0] "全息步枪聚焦光学组件"

#: .\items\gunmods.json
msgid ""
"A set of optics to concentrate the beam to make it more powerful, increasing"
" damage output."
msgstr "一套用于集中光束以增强威力的光学组件，可提高伤害输出。"

#: .\items\gunmods.json
msgid "lens"
msgstr "透镜"

#: .\items\gunmods.json
msgid "Holorifle advanced calibration"
msgid_plural "Holorifle advanced calibrations"
msgstr[0] "全息步枪高级校准组件"

#: .\items\gunmods.json
msgid ""
"A set of parts for the Holorifle that helps calibrate the beam trajectory, "
"improving accuracy."
msgstr "一套用于全息步枪的部件，可校准光束轨迹，提高精准度。"

#: .\items\gunmods.json
msgid "mechanism"
msgstr "机械装置"

#: .\items\gunmods.json
msgid "Holorifle reinforced components"
msgid_plural "Holorifle reinforced componentss"
msgstr[0] "全息步枪强化部件"

#: .\items\gunmods.json
msgid "A set of reinforced Holorifle parts designed to make it more reliable."
msgstr "一套强化过的全息步枪部件，旨在提高其可靠性。"

#: .\items\gunmods.json
msgid "Gauss rifle scope"
msgid_plural "Gauss rifle scopes"
msgstr[0] "高斯步枪瞄准镜"

#: .\items\gunmods.json
msgid ""
"A rifle scope designed specifically for the use with the Gauss rifle. Has a "
"blue-glowing lens to look through, helping with target identification, "
"allowing adjustable zoom and quick aiming."
msgstr "专为高斯步枪设计的步枪瞄准镜。配有发蓝光的镜片，有助于目标识别，支持变焦调节和快速瞄准。"

#: .\items\gunmods.json
msgctxt "gun_type_type"
msgid "gauss_rifle"
msgstr "高斯步枪"

#: .\items\materials.json
msgid "Cloud residue"
msgid_plural "Cloud residue"
msgstr[0] "云层残渣"

#. ~ Description for {'str_sp': 'Cloud residue'}
#: .\items\materials.json
msgid ""
"A portion of Sierra Madre toxic gas concentrated enough that it became "
"solidified, sticking itself to the surfaces. You could use it to experiment "
"a bit with a Cloud and possibly craft some useful stuff."
msgstr "一份浓度高到固化的锡耶拉马德雷毒气，附着在物体表面。你可以用它稍作实验，或许能制作出有用的物品。"

#: .\items\materials.json
msgid "turpentine"
msgid_plural "turpentine"
msgstr[0] "松节油"

#. ~ Description for {'str_sp': 'turpentine'}
#: .\items\materials.json
msgid "A flammable liquid used as a common solvent."
msgstr "一种易燃液体，常用作溶剂。"

#: .\items\misc.json
msgid "explosive collar"
msgid_plural "explosive collars"
msgstr[0] "爆炸项圈"

#. ~ Use action menu_text for {'str': 'explosive collar'}.
#: .\items\misc.json
msgid "Set the collar to explode"
msgstr "设置项圈引爆"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'explosive collar'}.
#: .\items\misc.json
msgid "You trigger the collar's explosive mechanism."
msgstr "你触发了项圈的爆炸机制。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'explosive collar'}
#: .\items\misc.json
msgid ""
"A sturdy, black metallic collar wrapping tightly around the neck of a person"
" unfortunate enough to be forced to wear it. Contains an explosive charge "
"ready to blow off the head. Can be set up ready to go off via compatible "
"radio signal. You don't want to wear it on yourself, right?..."
msgstr ""
"一个坚固的黑色金属项圈紧紧箍在不幸被迫佩戴者的脖子上。内含炸药，随时准备炸飞头颅。可通过兼容的无线电信号设置引爆。你肯定不想自己戴上它吧？……"

#. ~ Use action no_deactivate_msg for {'str': 'explosive collar'}.
#: .\items\misc.json
msgid ""
"The collar is about to explode. While the blast won't be very strong since "
"initially it's been designed to only blow the wearer's head off, it's still "
"strongly encouraged to get away from it."
msgstr "项圈即将爆炸。虽然爆炸威力不会太强——因为它最初设计仅用于炸飞佩戴者的头部——但仍强烈建议远离它。"

#. ~ Use action sound_msg for {'str': 'explosive collar'}.
#: .\items\misc.json
msgid "Beep."
msgstr "哔。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'explosive collar'}
#: .\items\misc.json
msgid ""
"The collar is constantly beeping, ready to blow up once its internal timer "
"reaches zero."
msgstr "项圈持续发出哔哔声，一旦内部计时器归零就会爆炸。"

#: .\items\misc.json
msgid "Sierra Madre chip"
msgid_plural "Sierra Madre chips"
msgstr[0] "马德雷筹码"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Sierra Madre chip'}
#: .\items\misc.json
msgid ""
"This is a golden chip from the Sierra Madre casino, intended for gambling "
"and collecting rewards at vending machines scattered around the resort. On "
"its heads there's a face of a woman and an acronym \"SM\". On the tails you "
"can see a portrait of a fancy-dressed woman holding the sign \"Begin again\""
" and a sign \"Sierra Madre\" under her feet."
msgstr ""
"这是来自马德雷赌场的金色筹码，用于赌博和在度假村各处自动售货机兑换奖励。正面印有女子面容和缩写“SM”。背面可见一位盛装女子手持“重新开始”标牌，脚下写着“马德雷”字样。"

#: .\items\misc.json
msgid "entertainer pass"
msgid_plural "entertainer passs"
msgstr[0] "演艺人员通行证"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'entertainer pass'}
#: .\items\misc.json
msgid ""
"This ID card once belonged to one of the entertainers working at Tampico "
"theater. Not of much use now, given the world ended and the security "
"personnel is purely holographic and in engagement mode."
msgstr "这张身份证曾属于坦皮科剧院的演艺人员。如今已无太大用处，毕竟世界已毁灭，安保人员全是全息影像且处于交战模式。"

#: .\items\misc.json
msgid "Sierra Madre gold bar"
msgid_plural "Sierra Madre gold bars"
msgstr[0] "马德雷金条"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Sierra Madre gold bar'}
#: .\items\misc.json
msgid ""
"A weighty gold bar from the vault of the Sierra Madre casino. Technically "
"worthless in a post-apocalyptic world, but the fact that it's from the "
"legendary Sierra Madre actually makes it valuable for some rich traders "
"willing to collect souvenirs."
msgstr "来自马德雷赌场金库的沉甸甸金条。在后末日世界本无实际价值，但因其出自传奇的马德雷，某些热衷收藏纪念品的富商反而视若珍宝。"

#: .\items\misc.json
msgid "bear trap fist HD springs"
msgid_plural "bear trap fist HD springss"
msgstr[0] "捕熊拳套HD弹簧"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'bear trap fist HD springs'}
#: .\items\misc.json
msgid ""
"A set of springs for the bear trap fist to make its claws more powerful."
msgstr "一套用于增强捕熊拳套爪击威力的弹簧。"

#: .\items\misc.json
msgid "laser pistol energy cell magazine"
msgid_plural "laser pistol energy cell magazines"
msgstr[0] "激光手枪能源电池弹匣"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'laser pistol energy cell magazine'}
#: .\items\misc.json
msgid "A 30 round magazine for laser pistols utilizing energy cells."
msgstr "适用于使用能源电池的激光手枪的30发弹匣。"

#: .\items\misc.json
msgid "Gauss rifle magazine"
msgid_plural "Gauss rifle magazines"
msgstr[0] "高斯步枪弹鼓"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Gauss rifle magazine'}
#: .\items\misc.json
msgid ""
"A drum capable of holding one pack of 5 microfusion cells designed to be "
"used specifically with the Gauss rifle."
msgstr "专为高斯步枪设计的弹鼓，可容纳一组5枚微型聚变电池。"

#: .\items\misc.json
msgid "skeleton"
msgid_plural "skeletons"
msgstr[0] "骸骨"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'skeleton'}
#: .\items\misc.json
msgid "A dead skeleton."
msgstr "一具死亡骸骨。"

#: .\items\misc.json
msgid "Sierra Madre chips inserting slot"
msgid_plural "Sierra Madre chips inserting slots"
msgstr[0] "马德雷筹码插入槽"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Sierra Madre chips inserting slot'}
#: .\items\misc.json
msgid "debug item"
msgstr "调试物品"

#: .\items\misc.json
msgid "Hologram visualisation"
msgid_plural "Hologram visualisations"
msgstr[0] "全息影像可视化"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Hologram visualisation'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Sierra Madre Vault console display'}
#: .\items\misc.json
msgid "If you see it it's one giant bug."
msgstr "如果你能看到这个，说明出现了重大漏洞。"

#: .\items\misc.json
msgid "Sierra Madre Vault console display"
msgid_plural "Sierra Madre Vault console displays"
msgstr[0] "马德雷金库控制台显示屏"

#: .\items\misc.json
msgid "Sierra Madre playing card"
msgid_plural "Sierra Madre playing cards"
msgstr[0] "马德雷扑克牌"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Sierra Madre playing card'}
#: .\items\misc.json
msgid "A playing card from an exclusive Sierra Madre deck."
msgstr "来自马德雷专属扑克牌组的一张牌。"

#: .\items\misc.json
msgid "Sierra Madre map"
msgid_plural "Sierra Madre maps"
msgstr[0] "马德雷地图"

#. ~ Use action message for {'str': 'Sierra Madre map'}.
#: .\items\misc.json
msgid ""
"You've heard of the Sierra Madre Casino. We all have, the legend, the "
"curses. Do you have what it takes to crack it open?"
msgstr "你听说过马德雷赌场。我们都听过那些传说与诅咒。你有能力揭开它的秘密吗？"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Sierra Madre map'}
#: .\items\misc.json
msgid ""
"Strange, mysterious hand-drawn map claiming to lead to the legendary Sierra "
"Madre, where the greatest treasure of the Old World is believed to be "
"buried."
msgstr "一张神秘的手绘地图，声称能指引前往传奇的马德雷——据信旧世界最伟大的宝藏就埋藏于此。"

#: .\items\weapons.json
msgid "Ghost's knife spear"
msgid_plural "Ghost's knife spears"
msgstr[0] "幽灵的刀矛"

#. ~ Description for {'str': "Ghost's knife spear"}
#: .\items\weapons.json
msgid ""
"A sturdy, menacing-looking knife spear Ghost People use to fight and hunt "
"with. While an improvised weapon by the concept itself, as far as the "
"execution goes, it doesn't feel like so. The sharp, large blade, apparently "
"made specifically with this kind of weapon in mind, is attached to the "
"thick, carefully cut pole with a several layers of tough rope, glue and "
"industrial-grade ducttape. One the one hand it's good to be armed with it, "
"on the other it's scary Sierra Madre is swarming with monsters using these "
"to kill their prey."
msgstr ""
"鬼族用于战斗和狩猎的坚固、外观凶险的刀矛。虽然从概念上讲是临时武器，但就制作工艺而言，却感觉并非如此。锋利宽大的刀刃显然是专门为此类武器打造的，通过多层坚韧绳索、胶水和工业级强力胶带固定在粗壮且精心切割的杆身上。一方面，装备它是件好事；另一方面，令人恐惧的是，马德雷山脉遍布着使用这种武器猎杀猎物的怪物。"

#: .\items\weapons.json
msgid "Ghost's clean knife spear"
msgid_plural "Ghost's clean knife spears"
msgstr[0] "鬼族的洁净刀矛"

#. ~ Description for {'str': "Ghost's clean knife spear"}
#: .\items\weapons.json
msgid ""
"This weapon executes the same concept as the standard Ghost's knife spear, "
"expect it's blade is the one from clean cosmic knife, combining the "
"advantages of both weapoons into one."
msgstr "这把武器与标准鬼族刀矛的设计理念相同，但其刀刃来自洁净的宇宙刀，将两种武器的优势合二为一。"

#: .\items\weapons.json
msgid "Ghost's knife spear poisoned with Cloud Kiss (weak)"
msgid_plural "Ghost's knife spears poisoned with Cloud Kiss (weak)"
msgstr[0] "涂有云吻之毒（弱效）的鬼族刀矛"

#. ~ Description for {'str': "Ghost's knife spear poisoned with Cloud Kiss
#. (weak)", 'str_pl': "Ghost's knife spears poisoned with Cloud Kiss (weak)"}
#. ~ Description for {'str': "Ghost's knife spear poisoned with Cloud Kiss
#. (potent)", 'str_pl': "Ghost's knife spears poisoned with Cloud Kiss
#. (potent)"}
#. ~ Description for {'str': "Ghost's knife spear poisoned with Cloud Kiss
#. (lethal)", 'str_pl': "Ghost's knife spears poisoned with Cloud Kiss
#. (lethal)"}
#: .\items\weapons.json
msgid ""
"A sturdy, menacing-looking knife spear Ghost People use to fight and hunt "
"with. While an improvised weapon by the concept itself, as far as the "
"execution goes, it doesn't feel like so. The sharp, large blade, apparently "
"made specifically with this kind of weapon in mind, is attached to the "
"thick, carefully cut pole with a several layers of tough rope, glue and "
"industrial-grade ducttape. One the one hand it's good to be armed with it, "
"on the other it's scary Sierra Madre is swarming with monsters using these "
"to kill their prey. It has been poisoned with the venom made out of the "
"Sierra Madre Cloud and thanks to it will poison your enemies, dealing "
"additional damage over time."
msgstr ""
"鬼族用于战斗和狩猎的坚固、外观凶险的刀矛。虽然从概念上讲是临时武器，但就制作工艺而言，却感觉并非如此。锋利宽大的刀刃显然是专门为此类武器打造的，通过多层坚韧绳索、胶水和工业级强力胶带固定在粗壮且精心切割的杆身上。一方面，装备它是件好事；另一方面，令人恐惧的是，马德雷山脉遍布着使用这种武器猎杀猎物的怪物。它已被马德雷山脉云雾制成的毒液淬毒，因此能毒害你的敌人，造成持续额外伤害。"

#: .\items\weapons.json
msgid "Ghost's knife spear poisoned with Cloud Kiss (potent)"
msgid_plural "Ghost's knife spears poisoned with Cloud Kiss (potent)"
msgstr[0] "涂有云吻之毒（强效）的鬼族刀矛"

#: .\items\weapons.json
msgid "Ghost's knife spear poisoned with Cloud Kiss (lethal)"
msgid_plural "Ghost's knife spears poisoned with Cloud Kiss (lethal)"
msgstr[0] "涂有云吻之毒（致命）的鬼族刀矛"

#: .\items\weapons.json
msgid "Ghost's throwing knife spear"
msgid_plural "Ghost's throwing knife spears"
msgstr[0] "鬼族的投掷刀矛"

#. ~ Description for {'str': "Ghost's throwing knife spear"}
#: .\items\weapons.json
msgid ""
"A lighter and shorter version of the knife spear used by Ghost People meant "
"for throwing. Was designed to deal powerful blows, but at a cost of being "
"rather fragile, as opposed to their main knife spears."
msgstr "鬼族使用的刀矛的轻量缩短版，专为投掷设计。旨在造成强力打击，但代价是相对脆弱，与其主战刀矛形成对比。"

#: .\items\weapons.json
msgid "bear trap fist"
msgid_plural "bear trap fists"
msgstr[0] "捕熊陷阱拳套"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'bear trap fist', 'str_pl': 'bear trap fists'}
#: .\items\weapons.json
msgid ""
"A small bear trap some Ghost People use as a weapon by strapping it to their"
" arm and clawing it at their prey. Its dark, sturdy teeth and the overall "
"concept itself fill you with fear you can't rationally explain."
msgstr "一些鬼族用作武器的小型捕熊陷阱，将其绑在手臂上抓向猎物。它暗沉坚固的利齿以及整体设计本身，让你充满一种无法理性解释的恐惧。"

#: .\items\weapons.json
msgid "bear trap fist poisoned with Cloud Kiss (weak)"
msgid_plural "bear trap fists poisoned with Cloud Kiss (weak)"
msgstr[0] "涂有云吻之毒（弱效）的捕熊陷阱拳套"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'bear trap fist poisoned with Cloud Kiss (weak)',
#. 'str_pl': 'bear trap fists poisoned with Cloud Kiss (weak)'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'bear trap fist poisoned with Cloud Kiss
#. (potent)', 'str_pl': 'bear trap fists poisoned with Cloud Kiss (potent)'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'bear trap fist poisoned with Cloud Kiss
#. (lethal)', 'str_pl': 'bear trap fists poisoned with Cloud Kiss (lethal)'}
#: .\items\weapons.json
msgid ""
"A small bear trap some Ghost People use as a weapon by strapping it to their"
" arm and clawing it at their prey. Its dark, sturdy teeth and the overall "
"concept itself fill you with fear you can't rationally explain. It has been "
"poisoned with the venom made out of the Sierra Madre Cloud and thanks to it "
"will poison your enemies, dealing additional damage over time."
msgstr ""
"一些鬼族用作武器的小型捕熊陷阱，将其绑在手臂上抓向猎物。它暗沉坚固的利齿以及整体设计本身，让你充满一种无法理性解释的恐惧。它已被马德雷山脉云雾制成的毒液淬毒，因此能毒害你的敌人，造成持续额外伤害。"

#: .\items\weapons.json
msgid "bear trap fist poisoned with Cloud Kiss (potent)"
msgid_plural "bear trap fists poisoned with Cloud Kiss (potent)"
msgstr[0] "涂有云吻之毒（强效）的捕熊陷阱拳套"

