"A mysterious man wanting to wipe the wasteland clean... Maybe he was normal "
"once, but now he's just a mere terrorist, all because he couldn't let go..."
msgstr "一个想要将废土清洗干净的神秘男人...也许他曾是个正常人，但现在他不过是个恐怖分子，全因他无法放下..."

