#: .\start\professions.json
msgctxt "profession_male"
msgid "Sierra Madre Treasure Hunter"
msgstr "马德雷山脉宝藏猎人"

#: .\start\professions.json
msgctxt "profession_female"
msgid "Sierra Madre Treasure Hunter"
msgstr "马德雷山脉宝藏猎人"

#. ~ Profession (male Sierra Madre Treasure Hunter) description
#: .\start\professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_male"
msgid ""
"You've heard of the Sierra Madre Casino. And so you've set, just like many "
"other fools before, to find it and crack it open, uncovering the legendary "
"treasure of the Old World buried within it."
msgstr "你听说过马德雷山脉赌场。于是你就像之前的许多傻瓜一样，决心找到并撬开它，揭开埋藏在其中的旧世界传奇宝藏。"

#. ~ Profession (female Sierra Madre Treasure Hunter) description
#: .\start\professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_female"
msgid ""
"You've heard of the Sierra Madre Casino. And so you've set, just like many "
"other fools before, to find it and crack it open, uncovering the legendary "
"treasure of the Old World buried within it."
msgstr "你听说过马德雷山脉赌场。于是你就像之前的许多傻瓜一样，决心找到并撬开它，揭开埋藏在其中的旧世界传奇宝藏。"

#. ~ Name for scenario 'Challenge - Heist of the Centuries' for a male
#. character
#: .\start\scenarios.json
msgctxt "scenario_male"
msgid "Challenge - Heist of the Centuries"
msgstr "挑战 - 世纪大劫案"

#. ~ Name for scenario 'Challenge - Heist of the Centuries' for a female
#. character
#: .\start\scenarios.json
msgctxt "scenario_female"
msgid "Challenge - Heist of the Centuries"
msgstr "挑战 - 世纪大劫案"

#. ~ Description for scenario 'Challenge - Heist of the Centuries' for a male
#. character.
#: .\start\scenarios.json
msgctxt "scen_desc_male"
msgid ""
"You've heard of the Sierra Madre Casino. We all have, the legend, the "
"curses. Some foolishness about it lying in the middle of a City of Dead. A "
"city of ghosts. Buried beneath a blood-red cloud... A bright, shining "
"monument luring treasure hunters to their doom. An illusion that you can "
"begin again, change your fortunes. Finding it, though, that's not the hard "
"part. It's letting go."
msgstr ""
"你听说过马德雷山脉赌场。我们都听说过，那个传说，那些诅咒。有些愚蠢的说法是它位于一座死亡之城的中心。一座鬼城。埋藏在血红色的云层之下……一座明亮闪耀的纪念碑，引诱寻宝者走向毁灭。一个你可以重新开始、改变命运的幻象。然而，找到它并不难。难的是放手。"

#. ~ Description for scenario 'Challenge - Heist of the Centuries' for a
#. female character.
#: .\start\scenarios.json
msgctxt "scen_desc_female"
msgid ""
"You've heard of the Sierra Madre Casino. We all have, the legend, the "
"curses. Some foolishness about it lying in the middle of a City of Dead. A "
"city of ghosts. Buried beneath a blood-red cloud... A bright, shining "
"monument luring treasure hunters to their doom. An illusion that you can "
"begin again, change your fortunes. Finding it, though, that's not the hard "
"part. It's letting go."
msgstr ""
"你听说过马德雷山脉赌场。我们都听说过，那个传说，那些诅咒。有些愚蠢的说法是它位于一座死亡之城的中心。一座鬼城。埋藏在血红色的云层之下……一座明亮闪耀的纪念碑，引诱寻宝者走向毁灭。一个你可以重新开始、改变命运的幻象。然而，找到它并不难。难的是放手。"

#. ~ Starting location for scenario 'Challenge - Heist of the Centuries'.
#: .\start\scenarios.json
msgctxt "start_name"
msgid "Sierra Madre"
msgstr "马德雷山脉"

#: .\terrain\furniture.json
msgid "Dean's secret stash"
msgstr "迪恩的秘密藏匿点"

#. ~ Description for Dean's secret stash
#: .\terrain\furniture.json
msgid ""
"A stash containing some useful stuff, left here by a survivor that once "
"walked these streets just like you..."
msgstr "一个藏匿着一些有用物品的藏匿点，由一位曾像你一样走过这些街道的幸存者留下……"

#: .\terrain\furniture.json
msgid "smash!"
msgstr "砸！"

#: .\terrain\furniture.json .\terrain\terrain.json
msgid "whump."
msgstr "砰。"

#: .\terrain\furniture.json
msgid "broken radio"
msgstr "损坏的收音机"

#. ~ Description for broken radio
#: .\terrain\furniture.json
msgid ""
"This radio, once capable of broadcasting all kinds of signals, now remains "
"broken. Upon closer look you notice a bullet hole in it."
msgstr "这台收音机曾经能够广播各种信号，现在却已损坏。仔细一看，你注意到上面有一个弹孔。"

#: .\terrain\furniture.json .\terrain\terrain.json
msgid "crunch!"
msgstr "嘎吱！"

#: .\terrain\furniture.json .\terrain\terrain.json
msgid "whack!"
msgstr "啪！"

#. ~ Description for Sierra Madre vending machine
#: .\terrain\furniture.json
msgid ""
"Sierra Madre vending machine... A form of matter assembler, accepts Sierra "
"Madre chips and then transforms them into all kinds of useful stuff. Having "
"certain code cards will allow you to unlock more interesting items to "
"purchase from it."
msgstr ""
"马德雷山脉自动售货机……一种物质组装器，接受马德雷山脉筹码，然后将它们转化为各种有用的物品。拥有特定的代码卡将允许你解锁更多有趣的物品进行购买。"

#. ~ Description for Sierra Madre hologram vendor
#. ~ Description for Vera Keyes' fountain hologram
#: .\terrain\furniture.json
msgid ""
"Sierra Madre hologram vendor, an autonomous worker for the guests to make "
"purchases or exchange various kinds of commodities."
msgstr "马德雷山脉全息售货员，一个为客人提供购买或交换各种商品的自主工作者。"

#. ~ Description for Gala control panel
#: .\terrain\furniture.json
msgid "Still operational terminal used to trigger and control the Gala Event."
msgstr "仍可操作的终端，用于触发和控制庆典活动。"

#: .\terrain\furniture.json
msgid "street lantern"
msgstr "街灯"

#. ~ Description for street lantern
#: .\terrain\furniture.json
msgid ""
"A simple street lantern providing some light for the dark night streets as "
"long as it has access to a power source. This one has been stylized to look "
"like lanterns from the late XIX or early XX century."
msgstr "一盏简单的街灯，只要接入电源，就能为黑暗的夜晚街道提供一些光亮。这一盏被设计成模仿十九世纪末或二十世纪初的灯笼风格。"

#: .\terrain\terrain.json
msgid "dried fountain"
msgstr "干涸的喷泉"

#. ~ Description for dried fountain
#: .\terrain\terrain.json
msgid ""
"A paved bed of a dried fountain, slowly but inevitably eroding due to lack "
"of maintenance."
msgstr "一个干涸喷泉的铺砌基座，由于缺乏维护，正在缓慢但不可避免地侵蚀。"

#: .\terrain\terrain.json
msgid "Sierra Madre Casino wall"
msgstr "马德雷山脉赌场墙壁"

#. ~ Description for Sierra Madre Casino wall
#: .\terrain\terrain.json
msgid ""
"An outer wall used in building of the Sierra Madre Casino. Truly "
"impenetrable - can survive several direct hits with nuclear warheads almost "
"unscratched."
msgstr "用于建造马德雷山脉赌场的外墙。真正坚不可摧——能够承受数次核弹头的直接命中而几乎毫发无损。"

#: .\terrain\terrain.json
msgid "Sierra Madre Casino roof"
msgstr "马德雷山脉赌场屋顶"

#. ~ Description for Sierra Madre Casino roof
#: .\terrain\terrain.json
msgid ""
"Roof covering the Sierra Madre Casino, made out of the same material as its "
"walls, making it indestructible."
msgstr "覆盖马德雷山脉赌场的屋顶，由与其墙壁相同的材料制成，使其坚不可摧。"

#: .\terrain\terrain.json
msgid "crash!"
msgstr "崩溃！"

#: .\terrain\terrain.json
msgid "bash!"
msgstr "猛击！"

#: .\terrain\terrain.json
msgid "open air"
msgstr "露天"

#. ~ Description for open air
#: .\terrain\terrain.json
msgid "This is open air."
msgstr "这里是露天环境。"

#: .\terrain\terrain.json
msgid "Sierra Madre Casino floor"
msgstr "锡耶纳马德雷赌场地板"

#. ~ Description for Sierra Madre Casino floor
#: .\terrain\terrain.json
msgid ""
"Red tiles out of which the floor inside the Sierra Madre Casino is made."
msgstr "锡耶纳马德雷赌场内部地板所用的红色瓷砖。"

#: .\terrain\terrain.json
msgid "SMASH!"
msgstr "砰！"

#: .\terrain\terrain.json
msgid "Sierra Madre Casino floor, with overhead light"
msgstr "锡耶纳马德雷赌场地板，带顶灯"

#. ~ Description for Sierra Madre Casino floor, with overhead light
#: .\terrain\terrain.json
msgid ""
"Red tiles out of which the floor inside the Sierra Madre Casino is made, "
"with a still-functioning light attached to the ceiling above."
msgstr "锡耶纳马德雷赌场内部地板所用的红色瓷砖，上方天花板上仍有一盏正常工作的灯。"

#: .\terrain\terrain.json
msgid "thump"
msgstr "重击声"

#: .\terrain\terrain.json
msgid "Sierra Madre red carpet"
msgstr "锡耶纳马德雷红地毯"

#. ~ Description for Sierra Madre red carpet
#: .\terrain\terrain.json
msgid ""
"Fancy and durable red carpet used to decorate the interiors of the Sierra "
"Madre Casino."
msgstr "用于装饰锡耶纳马德雷赌场内部的华丽耐用红地毯。"

#: .\terrain\terrain.json
msgid "locked Sierra Madre Casino entrance door"
msgstr "上锁的锡耶纳马德雷赌场入口门"

#. ~ Description for locked Sierra Madre Casino entrance door
#: .\terrain\terrain.json
msgid "entrance to the Sierra Madre Casino, locked and indestructible."
msgstr "锡耶纳马德雷赌场的入口，已上锁且无法破坏。"

#: .\terrain\terrain.json
msgid "Sierra Madre Casino entrance door"
msgstr "锡耶纳马德雷赌场入口门"

#. ~ Description for Sierra Madre Casino entrance door
#: .\terrain\terrain.json
msgid ""
"entrance to the Sierra Madre Casino, unlocked, but still indestructible."
msgstr "锡耶纳马德雷赌场的入口，已解锁，但仍无法破坏。"

#: .\terrain\terrain.json
msgid "open Sierra Madre Casino entrance door"
msgstr "打开的锡耶纳马德雷赌场入口门"

#. ~ Description for open Sierra Madre Casino entrance door
#: .\terrain\terrain.json
msgid "entrance to the Sierra Madre Casino, open, but still indestructible."
msgstr "锡耶纳马德雷赌场的入口，已打开，但仍无法破坏。"

#: .\terrain\terrain.json
msgid "locked Sierra Madre Casino door"
msgstr "上锁的锡耶纳马德雷赌场门"

#. ~ Description for locked Sierra Madre Casino door
#: .\terrain\terrain.json
msgid ""
"door to the more important interiors of the Sierra Madre Casino. Locked and "
"indestructible just like the entrance door."
msgstr "通往锡耶纳马德雷赌场更内部区域的门。与入口门一样，已上锁且无法破坏。"

#: .\terrain\terrain.json
msgid "Sierra Madre Casino door"
msgstr "锡耶纳马德雷赌场门"

#. ~ Description for Sierra Madre Casino door
#: .\terrain\terrain.json
msgid ""
"door to the more important interiors of the Sierra Madre Casino. "
"Indestructible just like the entrance door."
msgstr "通往锡耶纳马德雷赌场更内部区域的门。与入口门一样无法破坏。"

#: .\terrain\terrain.json
msgid "open Sierra Madre Casino door"
msgstr "打开的锡耶纳马德雷赌场门"

#. ~ Description for open Sierra Madre Casino door
#: .\terrain\terrain.json
msgid ""
"Sierra Madre Casino internal door, currently open, still indestructible."
msgstr "锡耶纳马德雷赌场内部门，当前已打开，仍无法破坏。"

#: .\terrain\terrain.json
msgid "locked Sierra Madre Vault door"
msgstr "上锁的锡耶纳马德雷金库门"

#. ~ Description for locked Sierra Madre Vault door
#: .\terrain\terrain.json
msgid "door to the legendary Sierra Madre Vault, locked and indestructible."
msgstr "通往传奇的锡耶纳马德雷金库的门，已上锁且无法破坏。"

#: .\terrain\terrain.json
msgid "Sierra Madre Vault door"
msgstr "锡耶纳马德雷金库门"

#. ~ Description for Sierra Madre Vault door
#: .\terrain\terrain.json
msgid ""
"door to the legendary Sierra Madre Vault, unlocked, but still "
"indestructible."
msgstr "通往传奇的锡耶纳马德雷金库的门，已解锁，但仍无法破坏。"

#: .\terrain\terrain.json
msgid "open Sierra Madre Vault door"
msgstr "打开的锡耶纳马德雷金库门"

#. ~ Description for open Sierra Madre Vault door
#: .\terrain\terrain.json
msgid ""
"door to the legendary Sierra Madre Vault, while indestructible, unlocked and"
" opened right in front of you, waiting for you to enter the Vault and crack "
"the Sierra Madre Treasure open..."
msgstr "通往传奇的锡耶纳马德雷金库的门，虽然无法破坏，但已解锁并打开在你面前，等待你进入金库，开启锡耶纳马德雷的宝藏……"

#: .\terrain\terrain.json
msgid "Sierra Madre Vault intercom"
msgstr "锡耶纳马德雷金库对讲机"

#. ~ Description for Sierra Madre Vault intercom
#: .\terrain\terrain.json
msgid ""
"The intercom located next to the Sierra Madre Vault, protecting it with a "
"voice password."
msgstr "位于锡耶纳马德雷金库旁的对讲机，通过语音密码保护金库。"

#. ~ Description for Sierra Madre Casino wall
#: .\terrain\terrain.json
msgid ""
"A solid brick wall used inside the Sierra Madre Casino. Years of "
"accumulating dirt made this once white wall yellow. From time to time you "
"can spot golden letters \"SM\" on it, the logo of the Sierra Madre."
msgstr "锡耶纳马德雷赌场内部使用的坚固砖墙。多年的积尘使这面曾经洁白的墙壁变黄。你偶尔能看到墙上金色的字母“SM”，那是锡耶纳马德雷的标志。"

#: .\terrain\terrain.json
msgid "slot machine"
msgstr "老虎机"

#. ~ Description for slot machine
#: .\terrain\terrain.json
msgid ""
"A machine with a bright screen flashing hypnotic promises of wealth.  If "
"gambling with your life on a daily basis isn't enough for you, you can also "
"gamble with this."
msgstr "一台带有明亮屏幕的机器，闪烁着催眠般的财富承诺。如果每天用生命赌博对你来说还不够，你也可以用它来赌一把。"

#: .\terrain\terrain.json
msgid "golden guard rail"
msgstr "金色护栏"

#. ~ Description for golden guard rail
#: .\terrain\terrain.json
msgid "A golden guard rail found inside the Sierra Madre Casino."
msgstr "在马德雷赌场内部发现的金色护栏。"

#: .\terrain\terrain.json
msgid "clang!"
msgstr "哐当！"

#: .\terrain\terrain.json
msgid "Sierra Madre armored window."
msgstr "马德雷装甲窗户。"

#. ~ Description for Sierra Madre armored window.
#: .\terrain\terrain.json
msgid ""
"A window appearing in the Sierra Madre suites. While it looks like any other"
" fancy window, it's supposed to withstand a direct hit by a nuclear warhead,"
" just like the entire Sierra Madre Casino. Tech used to design this wonder "
"comes, of course, from the Big Mountain research facility."
msgstr ""
"出现在马德雷套房中的窗户。虽然它看起来和其他豪华窗户没什么两样，但它应该能承受核弹头的直接打击，就像整个马德雷赌场一样。设计这一奇迹所用的技术，当然来自大山脉研究设施。"

#: .\terrain\terrain.json
msgid "Sierra Madre armored window without curtains"
msgstr "无窗帘的马德雷装甲窗户"

#. ~ Description for Sierra Madre armored window without curtains
#: .\terrain\terrain.json
msgid ""
"A window appearing in the Sierra Madre suites. While it looks like any other"
" fancy window (except it doesn't have curtains), it's supposed to withstand "
"a direct hit by a nuclear warhead, just like the entire Sierra Madre Casino."
" Tech used to design this wonder comes, of course, from the Big Mountain "
"research facility."
msgstr ""
"出现在马德雷套房中的窗户。虽然它看起来和其他豪华窗户没什么区别（除了没有窗帘），但它应该能承受核弹头的直接打击，就像整个马德雷赌场一样。设计这一奇迹所用的技术，当然来自大山脉研究设施。"

#: .\terrain\terrain.json
msgid "Sierra Madre armored window with closed curtains"
msgstr "带闭合窗帘的马德雷装甲窗户"

#. ~ Description for Sierra Madre armored window with closed curtains
#: .\terrain\terrain.json
msgid ""
"A window appearing in the Sierra Madre suites. While it looks like any other"
" fancy window with closed curtains would, it's supposed to withstand a "
"direct hit by a nuclear warhead, just like the entire Sierra Madre Casino. "
"Tech used to design this wonder comes, of course, from the Big Mountain "
"research facility."
msgstr ""
"出现在马德雷套房中的窗户。虽然它看起来和其他带闭合窗帘的豪华窗户一样，但它应该能承受核弹头的直接打击，就像整个马德雷赌场一样。设计这一奇迹所用的技术，当然来自大山脉研究设施。"

#: .\terrain\terrain.json
msgid "picket fence"
msgstr "尖桩篱栅"

#. ~ Description for picket fence
#: .\terrain\terrain.json
msgid ""
"A barrier made of wood, it's nothing complicated.  Mildly suggests where not"
" to go."
msgstr "用木头制成的屏障，没什么复杂的。温和地提示哪些地方不该去。"

#: .\terrain\terrain.json
msgid "crack."
msgstr "咔嚓。"

#: .\terrain\terrain.json
msgid "wham."
msgstr "砰。"

#: .\terrain\terrain.json
msgid "fence post"
msgstr "篱笆桩"

#. ~ Description for fence post
#: .\terrain\terrain.json
msgid ""
"A couple of posts that support the fence.  They look alone without the "
"fence."
msgstr "支撑篱笆的几个桩子。没有篱笆它们看起来孤零零的。"

#: .\terrain\terrain.json
msgid "Sierra Madre toxic gas"
msgstr "马德雷毒气"

#: .\terrain\terrain.json
msgid "Sierra Madre Cloud"
msgstr "马德雷云"

#: .\terrain\terrain.json
msgid "Sierra Madre Vault floor"
msgstr "马德雷金库地板"

#. ~ Description for Sierra Madre Vault floor
#: .\terrain\terrain.json
msgid ""
"The floor used to cover the ground of the Sierra Madre legendary vault, made"
" of the strongest metal alloys ever produced by humans."
msgstr "用于覆盖马德雷传奇金库地面的地板，由人类有史以来生产的最强金属合金制成。"

#. ~ Description for Sierra Madre Vault floor
#: .\terrain\terrain.json
msgid ""
"The floor used to cover the ground of the Sierra Madre legendary vault, made"
" of the strongest metal alloys ever produced by humans, with a still-"
"functioning light attached to the ceiling above."
msgstr "用于覆盖马德雷传奇金库地面的地板，由人类有史以来生产的最强金属合金制成，天花板上还附有一个仍在运作的灯。"

#: .\terrain\terrain.json
msgid "Sierra Madre Vault wall"
msgstr "马德雷金库墙壁"

#. ~ Description for Sierra Madre Vault wall
#: .\terrain\terrain.json
msgid ""
"Thick, practically indestructible wall used to protect the Sierra Madre "
"Vault. Even tougher than the outer walls of the Casino, this one can sustain"
" direct hits from at least a dozen nuclear warheads unscratched."
msgstr "用于保护马德雷金库的厚重、几乎坚不可摧的墙壁。甚至比赌场的外墙还要坚固，这面墙可以承受至少十几枚核弹头的直接打击而毫发无损。"

#: .\terrain\terrain.json
msgid "Sierra Madre Vault interior door"
msgstr "马德雷金库内部门"

#. ~ Description for Sierra Madre Vault interior door
#: .\terrain\terrain.json
msgid ""
"Closed indestructible door separating the interiors of the Sierra Madre "
"Vault."
msgstr "分隔马德雷金库内部的闭合式坚不可摧的门。"

#: .\terrain\terrain.json
msgid "open Sierra Madre Vault interior door"
msgstr "打开的马德雷金库内部门"

#. ~ Description for open Sierra Madre Vault interior door
#: .\terrain\terrain.json
msgid ""
"Opened indestructible door separating the interiors of the Sierra Madre "
"Vault."
msgstr "已打开的分隔马德雷金库内部的坚不可摧的门。"

#: .\terrain\terrain.json
msgid "Sierra Madre Vault glass wall"
msgstr "马德雷金库玻璃墙"

#. ~ Description for Sierra Madre Vault glass wall
#: .\terrain\terrain.json
msgid ""
"Super resistant type of ballistic glass developed at Big Mountain research "
"facility. As everything else used to build the Sierra Madre casino, "
"especially its vault, it's designed to withstand direct hit by a nuclear "
"warhead."
msgstr "在大山脉研究设施开发的超级抗冲击型防弹玻璃。与用于建造马德雷赌场，尤其是其金库的所有其他材料一样，它被设计成能承受核弹头的直接打击。"

#: .\terrain\terrain.json
msgid "high gauge pipe"
msgstr "大口径管道"

#. ~ Description for high gauge pipe
#: .\terrain\terrain.json
msgid "This is a section of high gauge pipe."
msgstr "这是一段大口径管道。"

#: .\terrain\terrain.json
msgid "metal screeching!"
msgstr "金属尖啸声！"

#. ~ Description for locked Sierra Madre Vault door
#: .\terrain\terrain.json
msgid ""
"door to the legendary Sierra Madre Vault, permanently locked due to vault's "
"trap activation, turning it from a vault into a coffin. YOUR coffin..."
msgstr "通往传奇马德雷金库的门，由于金库陷阱激活而永久锁死，使其从金库变成了棺材。你的棺材……"
